1
00:02:45,208 --> 00:02:47,750
参见玉帝⋯
Greetings to your highness

2
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:50,521
众卿家大发雷霆　所为何事
Ministers, why are you so mad?

3
00:02:50,521 --> 00:02:51,666
王母　你先讲
Queen Mother, you first

4
00:02:51,666 --> 00:02:53,271
玉帝啊　降龙罗汉
Your highness, Dragon Fighter Lo Han stole all the peaches…

5
00:02:53,271 --> 00:02:54,896
把我那棵蟠桃树上的蟠桃
Your highness, Dragon Fighter Lo Han stole all the peaches…

6
00:02:54,896 --> 00:02:56,979
全都偷去给牛郎的牛吃了
…from my peach tree for the Cowherd's cows

7
00:02:56,979 --> 00:02:58,687
还不止呢
Not only that, he also conspired with Magpie to arrange…

8
00:02:58,687 --> 00:03:00,229
他还串通那些喜鹊天天架起鹊桥
…the Cowherd & Spinster Maid rendezvous on the bridge

9
00:03:00,229 --> 00:03:01,687
让牛郎织女幽会　丑大了
…the Cowherd & Spinster Maid rendezvous on the bridge

10
00:03:01,687 --> 00:03:02,667
已经生下一打孩子了
Damn it! They've bred lots of children now

11
00:03:02,667 --> 00:03:04,167
哇
Damn it! They've bred lots of children now

12
00:03:04,167 --> 00:03:06,250
玉帝啊　向来凡间男女关系
Your highness, all along I've handled…

13
00:03:06,250 --> 00:03:07,437
一向由我来掌管
…lovers' relationships in the mortal world

14
00:03:07,437 --> 00:03:09,083
谁知他来到这里乱搞一通
Who would have thought he'd mess it up,

15
00:03:09,083 --> 00:03:10,625
搞得皇帝要去追〝野鸡〞
such that the emperor woos a whore,

16
00:03:10,625 --> 00:03:13,145
堂堂一个公主要跟乞丐私奔呢
and a princess elopes with a beggar

17
00:03:13,145 --> 00:03:14,437
我才说了他两句
I reprimanded him gently,

18
00:03:14,437 --> 00:03:16,937
他就偷了我的哮天犬　煮了吃了
he then stole my Heavenly Dog and braised it with bamboo shoots

19
00:03:16,937 --> 00:03:18,625
嗯　你又是什么人呢
Now who might you be?

20
00:03:18,625 --> 00:03:20,250
在下二郎神
I'm God No. 2

21
00:03:20,250 --> 00:03:21,625
玉帝　我这只眼
Your highness, my eye was also blinded by that bastard

22
00:03:21,625 --> 00:03:23,083
也是被那王八蛋给弄瞎的
Your highness, my eye was also blinded by that bastard

23
00:03:23,542 --> 00:03:25,708
这一只呢也是哮天犬的替身
This is just a substitute for Heavenly Dog

24
00:03:27,083 --> 00:03:29,167
国有国法　天有天条
Law and order must be enforced

25
00:03:29,167 --> 00:03:30,854
这个降龙目无王法
This Dragon Fighter is outrageous

26
00:03:30,854 --> 00:03:32,583
我希望玉帝批准我揍他
I hope your highness permits me to beat him up

27
00:03:32,625 --> 00:03:35,187
哼　财神　你也不必这么冲动啊
God of Fortune, stay calm

28
00:03:35,187 --> 00:03:36,667
哼　这些都是小事
These are small matters.

29
00:03:36,667 --> 00:03:38,541
他偷了我的生死簿　改得一塌糊涂
He stole my Book of Destiny and messed it up

30
00:03:38,541 --> 00:03:40,083
凡间已经十八年没死过人了
There hasn't been a death in 18 years

31
00:03:40,083 --> 00:03:41,271
弄得那些仵作都没事做
Those undertakers are out of work,

32
00:03:41,271 --> 00:03:42,770
还出了个五六百岁的人魔
and there's a centuries-old man

33
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:44,167
玉帝　你不摆平这个混蛋
Your highness, if you can't control him,

34
00:03:44,167 --> 00:03:45,542
我阎王一定告到九重天　小事化大
I'll bring this up with the Ninth Heaven

35
00:03:45,542 --> 00:03:46,917
我阎王一定告到九重天　小事化大
and make a great fuss

36
00:03:46,958 --> 00:03:49,479
来人呢　替我抓降龙上殿
Guards, summon Dragon Fighter to the palace

37
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:50,375
是
Yes

38
00:03:52,875 --> 00:03:56,042
哎⋯哎哟⋯不要这么用劲儿嘛
Hey… not so hard

39
00:03:56,083 --> 00:03:58,187
我正在睡午觉
I'm taking a nap, brother

40
00:03:58,187 --> 00:03:59,979
怎么　大家都来了　各位
Hey… everybody is here

41
00:03:59,979 --> 00:04:01,833
怎么　大家都来了　各位
What?

42
00:04:01,833 --> 00:04:04,042
你又不是降龙　你是伏虎　你来干吗
You're not Dragon Fighter, you're Tiger Fighter

43
00:04:04,125 --> 00:04:06,875
都一样嘛　降龙伏虎都一样嘛
It's just the same Dragon and Tiger are the same

44
00:04:06,875 --> 00:04:07,417
伏虎
Tiger Fighter

45
00:04:07,417 --> 00:04:08,187
哎　是　玉帝
Yes, your highness

46
00:04:08,187 --> 00:04:10,042
没你的事　你干吗上来呀
It doesn't concern you. Why are you here?

47
00:04:10,042 --> 00:04:12,437
哎　我是代表降龙来跟大家道歉的
I represent Dragon Fighter to apologize to you all

48
00:04:12,437 --> 00:04:13,541
你这么讲义气　难道你也有份
You speak so loyally,

49
00:04:13,541 --> 00:04:14,770
你这么讲义气　难道你也有份
are you also a part of this?

50
00:04:14,770 --> 00:04:16,458
哎⋯不关我的事啊
Hey! What has it to do with me? I…

51
00:04:16,458 --> 00:04:19,583
哎　神仙就大了
Do you think fairies can get away with everything?

52
00:04:21,917 --> 00:04:23,542
Ai! Aiya…

53
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:43,792
伏虎　你真是个管家婆
Tiger Fighter, you really are interfering,

54
00:04:43,792 --> 00:04:44,708
不过你还挺讲义气　我心领了
yet you're a loyal friend.

55
00:04:44,708 --> 00:04:45,833
不过你还挺讲义气　我心领了
I appreciate it

56
00:04:45,833 --> 00:04:46,896
哎　谢谢⋯
Thanks…

57
00:04:46,896 --> 00:04:48,604
哎　照目前情形看起来
Hey, as things stand,

58
00:04:48,604 --> 00:04:50,625
随便认个错马上走算了
just make an apology and leave

59
00:04:50,625 --> 00:04:51,875
随便认错就想走
Do you think you can leave just by saying sorry?

60
00:04:51,875 --> 00:04:54,187
我们俩兄弟聊天　几时轮到你插嘴
Who are you to interrupt our conversation?

61
00:04:54,187 --> 00:04:56,021
嘿呀　你这个灶君
God of Hearth, each year-end… …you seek advantage in the mortal world,

62
00:04:56,021 --> 00:04:56,958
每逢年尾就想在下面搞便宜

63
00:04:56,958 --> 00:04:58,666
人家不给你
and speak ill of those families who gave you less

64
00:04:58,666 --> 00:04:59,375
你就到上面来说人家不是　插他
- Poke him    - Poke him

65
00:04:59,375 --> 00:05:00,437
插他
- Poke him    - Poke him

66
00:05:00,437 --> 00:05:02,625
啊　刚才插完好痛　现在又要插
Hey! You just did and it still hurts, don't poke again

67
00:05:02,625 --> 00:05:03,229
You, a petty Lo Han,

68
00:05:03,229 --> 00:05:05,041
小小一个罗汉　什么事情你都要管
poke your nose in everybody's business

69
00:05:05,041 --> 00:05:07,145
岂有此理　你偷吃我的蟠桃　赔来
Outrageous! You better compensate me

70
00:05:07,145 --> 00:05:07,583
for the stolen peaches

71
00:05:07,583 --> 00:05:10,125
王母　吃一点人家也没说什么
Queen Mother, what's the big deal to share some to others?

72
00:05:10,125 --> 00:05:10,833
什么
What?

73
00:05:10,833 --> 00:05:12,250
那蟠桃也该吃腻了吧
You must get fed up with peaches on your birthday each year

74
00:05:12,250 --> 00:05:12,854
什么
What?

75
00:05:12,854 --> 00:05:14,146
今年换换口味吃香蕉好了
Why not have a change and eat bananas this year

76
00:05:14,146 --> 00:05:15,125
啊
What?

77
00:05:16,333 --> 00:05:16,916
What?

78
00:05:16,916 --> 00:05:18,437
干吗　不服气就冲我来
Tell me frankly if you're still angry

79
00:05:18,437 --> 00:05:19,729
不要叫你的狗在那边乱吠
Don't have your dog howl for you

80
00:05:19,729 --> 00:05:21,125
别以为换了一只斑点我就不敢吃
Don't think just because he has spots

81
00:05:21,125 --> 00:05:22,562
我照吃不误　到哪一个了
I can sock all the same, I'm telling you

82
00:05:22,562 --> 00:05:24,062
我照吃不误　到哪一个了
Who's next?

83
00:05:24,062 --> 00:05:25,500
到哪一个了　就你好了
You will do

84
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:27,729
You Moon Match-maker,

85
00:05:27,729 --> 00:05:30,396
你这个月老　仗着几根破烂红绳
you fool humans with several red strings

86
00:05:30,396 --> 00:05:31,042
没事就胡牵乱扯

87
00:05:31,417 --> 00:05:33,583
就好像梁山伯与祝英台
Take for instance the Butterfly Lovers,

88
00:05:33,583 --> 00:05:35,541
为什么不肯把他们拴在一起
why not tie them together?

89
00:05:35,541 --> 00:05:37,271
搞得他们扑坟吐血
Instead you brought them a tragic ending,

90
00:05:37,271 --> 00:05:38,875
他们哪里对不起你了
what have they done to you to deserve this?

91
00:05:39,083 --> 00:05:41,729
我说你老了　没事就退休吧
You're old, you should retire…

92
00:05:41,729 --> 00:05:42,687
…before you make a mess Who knows, you may make wacky matches…

93
00:05:42,687 --> 00:05:43,458
不然将来牵错了红绳

94
00:05:43,458 --> 00:05:45,791
弄得男跟男　女跟女
…say like a man with a man, a woman with a woman,

95
00:05:45,791 --> 00:05:48,021
再弄下去　人跟猪　蟑螂配牛了
or even a man with a pig, a roach with a cow

96
00:05:48,021 --> 00:05:49,604
最惨的是蚂蚁跟大象啊
- Worst of all would be a lotus root with a rock    - Yes

97
00:05:49,604 --> 00:05:50,854
哎　插他
Poke him

98
00:05:50,854 --> 00:05:52,708
哎　人家年纪不小了　不要欺负他
He's old, spare him

99
00:05:52,708 --> 00:05:54,083
哎呀　你想管闲事吗　阎罗王
King of Hades, are you standing up for him?

100
00:05:54,083 --> 00:05:54,875
插他了
Poke him

101
00:05:54,875 --> 00:05:57,687
不要碰面就插　我们是讲道理的
Don't keep saying poke, we should be reasonable

102
00:05:57,687 --> 00:05:58,229
Your hand…

103
00:05:58,229 --> 00:05:59,437
为什么凡间有个女子
Why there's a woman in the mortal world who bore 16 daughters…

104
00:05:59,437 --> 00:06:00,771
连生了十六个女儿
Why there's a woman in the mortal world who bore 16 daughters…

105
00:06:00,771 --> 00:06:03,042
就不肯给她一个儿子　为什么
…and was denied a boy? Why?

106
00:06:03,958 --> 00:06:07,750
搞得那个女的终于想不开　跳海自尽
Consequently she jumped into the sea to kill herself

107
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,542
啊

108
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:13,417
到了下面　他还说她是枉死的
Even in hell, he accused her of innocent death,

109
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:16,562
把她丢到油锅里炸得跟麻花似的
flung her into a frying pan

110
00:06:16,562 --> 00:06:18,708
and fried her to a crisp

111
00:06:18,958 --> 00:06:22,375
你说天理何在呀
Do you think there's justice?

112
00:06:22,375 --> 00:06:24,750
降龙⋯
Lung… Dragon Fighter…

113
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,875
昏过去也没有用啊
Fainting is no use.

114
00:06:25,875 --> 00:06:27,708
凡人的命运早已经成定数　并无不妥
People's fate is predestined

115
00:06:27,708 --> 00:06:29,667
凡人的命运早已经成定数　并无不妥
There's nothing wrong about it

116
00:06:29,667 --> 00:06:31,667
由不得你在这儿无理取闹
So you shouldn't make trouble here

117
00:06:31,667 --> 00:06:33,833
我只是照例执行
- We're only carrying out orders    - Your highness…

118
00:06:33,833 --> 00:06:34,271
哎　我⋯

119
00:06:34,271 --> 00:06:34,771
Carrying out orders?

120
00:06:34,771 --> 00:06:36,354
谁说照例执行　谁订的令
Who set them?

121
00:06:36,354 --> 00:06:37,875
谁说一定是对的
Who dares to say it must be right?

122
00:06:38,333 --> 00:06:39,812
常言道天外有天
A saying goes, ‘There are other heavens’

123
00:06:39,812 --> 00:06:40,958
玉帝　你定的例
Your highness, if your rules…

124
00:06:40,958 --> 00:06:43,020
要是让九重天的菩萨给听见
were known by Bodhisattva in the Ninth Heaven,

125
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:44,979
只怕会是白痴说笑话
she'll think this is a joke of a moron

126
00:06:44,979 --> 00:06:46,187
太过分了
This is out of line

127
00:06:46,187 --> 00:06:48,250
玉帝　各位仙友
Your highness, fairies,

128
00:06:48,250 --> 00:06:51,208
本人觉得降龙罗汉实在太嚣张了
reckon Dragon Fighter Lo Han is just too rampant

129
00:06:51,208 --> 00:06:53,042
我财神为了顾全大局
I think, for everybody's advantage,

130
00:06:53,042 --> 00:06:54,542
请玉帝批准我跟他单挑
please allow me to fight him one on one

131
00:06:54,542 --> 00:07:00,979
笑死人了　你打得过他吗
- Haha…    - Shut up! You better shut up

132
00:07:00,979 --> 00:07:01,562
我要跟他单挑

133
00:07:01,562 --> 00:07:02,875
哎　算了⋯
- I want to fight him one on one    - Don't kill him

134
00:07:02,875 --> 00:07:03,833
我要跟他拼了　我不会放过他的
I'll not show him mercy

135
00:07:03,833 --> 00:07:04,833
我要跟他拼了　我不会放过他的
I won't let you go

136
00:07:04,833 --> 00:07:05,937
哎⋯吓死我⋯
Scare me

137
00:07:05,937 --> 00:07:08,458
听着　就算天条有什么不对
Listen! Even if there's a loophole in the laws of Heaven,

138
00:07:08,458 --> 00:07:10,125
总有一条可以定你们的罪
there must be one that convicts you

139
00:07:10,375 --> 00:07:11,854
押他们到凡间去
Escort them to the mortal world

140
00:07:11,854 --> 00:07:13,854
一个做猪　一个做狗
and make them a pig and a dog

141
00:07:13,854 --> 00:07:15,917
十世不得轮回
No transmigration for them in 10 lifetimes

142
00:07:16,458 --> 00:07:17,333
且慢
Wait

143
00:07:17,333 --> 00:07:18,208
什么事
What is it?

144
00:07:18,208 --> 00:07:19,625
你说做就做啊
Is your word final?

145
00:07:19,625 --> 00:07:20,625
我说就算
Sure

146
00:07:20,917 --> 00:07:22,979
我说你做蟑螂　你怎么说
I say you'll be a roach, let's go together

147
00:07:22,979 --> 00:07:25,791
押啊⋯押他们下去
Escort them down

148
00:07:25,791 --> 00:07:26,208
What?

149
00:07:26,208 --> 00:07:27,833
啊　哎　慢点　观音来了
Wait! Don't…

150
00:08:07,625 --> 00:08:10,000
参见大士⋯
Greetings to Goddess

151
00:08:10,083 --> 00:08:13,833
玉帝　我们每一位成仙至今
Heavenly Highness, each one of us has been a fairy…

152
00:08:13,917 --> 00:08:16,500
少说也有个万二八千年了
…for at least ten of thousands of years

153
00:08:17,083 --> 00:08:22,187
世情种种　凡间一切在我们来说
Worldly affairs to us…

154
00:08:22,187 --> 00:08:23,104
是遥远而微不足道

155
00:08:23,104 --> 00:08:26,417
今日被降龙罗汉这么一闹
…are distant and trivial

156
00:08:26,583 --> 00:08:29,083
或者是一个机缘
The mess Dragon Fighter Lo Han has caused today

157
00:08:29,083 --> 00:08:31,312
为什么不借这个机缘
might be an opportunity

158
00:08:31,312 --> 00:08:32,229
来了解一下凡人

159
00:08:32,229 --> 00:08:34,896
是不是仍然那么愚昧无知
Why not use it to understand the mortal world?

160
00:08:34,896 --> 00:08:36,229
抑或有所进步呢
To see if humans are still dumb and ignorant,

161
00:08:36,229 --> 00:08:37,729
抑或有所进步呢
or they have progressed?

162
00:08:37,729 --> 00:08:41,125
啊　听观音大士说话真是好听啊
Goddess of Mercy speaks well

163
00:08:41,125 --> 00:08:42,270
哎　舒服　舒服
What a relief…

164
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:42,875
大士
Goddess,

165
00:08:42,875 --> 00:08:45,083
这小子以替人家打抱不平为借口
this kid offends a superior…

166
00:08:45,083 --> 00:08:46,333
以下犯上
…under the pretext of fighting injustice

167
00:08:46,333 --> 00:08:47,958
你不要乱说话　阎罗王
Stop speaking nonsense, King of Hades

168
00:08:47,958 --> 00:08:49,666
慢点　大士自有分寸
Matters will be taken care of by the Goddess

169
00:08:49,666 --> 00:08:51,625
降龙　你做了这么多的事情
Dragon Fighter, what's your purpose of doing this?

170
00:08:51,625 --> 00:08:53,625
目的何在
Dragon Fighter, what's your purpose of doing this?

171
00:08:54,208 --> 00:08:57,395
我只是想让这一班高高在上的神仙
I want these fairies to get off their high horses,

172
00:08:57,395 --> 00:09:00,042
能够好好地真正地体验一下凡人
and experience the mortal world

173
00:09:00,875 --> 00:09:03,292
因为这些凡人只有几十年的命
Humans only live for a few decades,

174
00:09:03,292 --> 00:09:05,708
不要因为做错了一两件事就翻不了身
and they shouldn't be condemned for a mistake or two

175
00:09:06,167 --> 00:09:07,625
因为小弟我相信
Because, according to my opinion,

176
00:09:08,458 --> 00:09:11,000
无论他们是多么的笨　多么的无知
regardless of how ignorant and dumb they are,

177
00:09:11,167 --> 00:09:13,125
怎么凶　怎么该死也好
how evil and deserving of death,

178
00:09:13,417 --> 00:09:16,208
始终都是⋯
they are after all… after all…

179
00:09:16,208 --> 00:09:18,854
是这个⋯
they are after all… after all…

180
00:09:18,854 --> 00:09:20,354
讲啊⋯快说呀⋯
After what…

181
00:09:20,354 --> 00:09:22,000
讲啊⋯快说呀⋯
Go on

182
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,979
哎　是这个⋯
I mean… after all…

183
00:09:24,979 --> 00:09:26,875
都是人间有情
Subject to sympathy and love

184
00:09:28,125 --> 00:09:29,708
是不是　降龙
Right, Dragon Fighter?

185
00:09:30,375 --> 00:09:32,333
是啊　就是这样
Yes, that's it

186
00:09:32,333 --> 00:09:33,187
哎　我看就由你开始

187
00:09:33,187 --> 00:09:35,125
亲自下凡间去体验一下
Let's begin with you, going down to the mortal world

188
00:09:35,125 --> 00:09:36,687
你有没有这个胆量啊
to experience it. Alright?

189
00:09:36,687 --> 00:09:38,625
哟　我怕你啊　我正有此意
In fact that's what I intend to do

190
00:09:38,625 --> 00:09:39,875
那你拿什么证明呢
How are you going to prove it?

191
00:09:39,875 --> 00:09:41,875
我已经选了三个人
We've chosen 3 people

192
00:09:41,875 --> 00:09:44,583
这三个人的命运已经注定了
with predestined fates

193
00:09:44,583 --> 00:09:46,479
一个做九世乞丐
One will be a beggar for 9 lives

194
00:09:46,479 --> 00:09:48,354
一个做九世〝野鸡〞
One a prostitute for 9 lives,

195
00:09:48,354 --> 00:09:50,333
一个做九世恶人
and one a villain for 9 lives

196
00:09:50,333 --> 00:09:50,687
Dragon Fighter,

197
00:09:50,687 --> 00:09:53,542
如果你能够改变这三个人命运的话
if you can change their fates,

198
00:09:53,542 --> 00:09:54,958
就算你赢
then you win

199
00:09:54,958 --> 00:09:56,916
你说我们神仙都这么坏
Since you despise gods, alright,

200
00:09:56,916 --> 00:09:58,729
好　你就用凡人的身份下去
you'll go as a layman…

201
00:09:58,729 --> 00:09:59,792
不准用法力
…and not allowed to use magic

202
00:09:59,792 --> 00:10:01,229
啊⋯不用法力⋯
No magic?

203
00:10:01,229 --> 00:10:03,104
不用法力也是对的
That's right, Dragon Fighter

204
00:10:03,104 --> 00:10:05,375
降龙　就用你的诚意去感化他们
Use your sincerity to reform them

205
00:10:05,375 --> 00:10:07,917
好　我保证不会让你失望
Okay, I'll not fail you

206
00:10:08,958 --> 00:10:09,917
你等我
Wait for me

207
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,750
我就给你三天的时间
I'll give you 3 days

208
00:10:12,458 --> 00:10:13,916
谢谢　不过两天半就够了
Thanks

209
00:10:13,916 --> 00:10:15,375
谢谢　不过两天半就够了
But two and a half days will do

210
00:10:17,542 --> 00:10:19,292
(Southern Heaven Gate)

211
00:10:19,292 --> 00:10:19,771
你不一定要听

212
00:10:19,771 --> 00:10:22,479
但是今天我所说的一切
You don't have to listen

213
00:10:22,479 --> 00:10:24,021
将来如果你不照着做
but if you don't act accordingly,

214
00:10:24,021 --> 00:10:26,250
就不要妄想重返天庭
don't expect to return to Heaven

215
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:28,583
第一　除非你有公文批准
Firstly, unless you have the official permit,

216
00:10:28,583 --> 00:10:30,542
否则不能擅自进入天庭
you can't enter Heaven

217
00:10:30,542 --> 00:10:33,417
第二　你不可以带任何的法力下去
Secondly, you can't take magic powers with you

218
00:10:36,083 --> 00:10:37,895
阿龙⋯一路顺风
Ah Lung… Lung

219
00:10:37,895 --> 00:10:39,604
阿龙⋯一路顺风
Bon voyage

220
00:10:39,604 --> 00:10:40,562
彼此　彼此
Same to you

221
00:10:40,562 --> 00:10:42,041
好兄弟啊
Good brothers

222
00:10:42,041 --> 00:10:43,729
好兄弟　还有什么话跟我说
What else do you have for me?

223
00:10:43,729 --> 00:10:45,395
你死定了　你打也不会打
You're dead

224
00:10:45,395 --> 00:10:46,562
你死定了　你打也不会打
You can't fight and can't use magic

225
00:10:46,562 --> 00:10:48,583
法力也不准用　你到下面去死定了
You're bound to die in the mortal world

226
00:10:48,583 --> 00:10:49,270
谢谢
Thanks

227
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,083
不用客气
- Don't mention it    - Dragon Fighter,

228
00:10:50,083 --> 00:10:52,292
降龙　你不会死的
you won't die

229
00:10:52,292 --> 00:10:54,145
你在凡间轮回的时候
When you re-incarnate in the mortal world,

230
00:10:54,145 --> 00:10:55,729
留下了一个金身
a golden body has been left behind

231
00:10:55,729 --> 00:10:57,917
只要找到金身合而为一
Once you find and combine with it,

232
00:10:57,917 --> 00:10:59,833
就可以保住肉身不灭
you can preserve your physical body,

233
00:10:59,833 --> 00:11:01,500
可以穿梭阴阳间
and transmigrate between the mortal and spiritual worlds

234
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:04,250
也要靠它才能够返回天庭
Besides, with it you can return to Heaven too

235
00:11:04,708 --> 00:11:06,125
实在太好了
Splendid

236
00:11:06,292 --> 00:11:08,542
这次的旅程险阻重重
This journey will be filled with danger

237
00:11:08,542 --> 00:11:10,792
送你一把心想事成扇
I'll present you with a Fan of Wishes…

238
00:11:11,292 --> 00:11:13,625
这把扇每天只能够用三次
…which can only be used 3 times daily

239
00:11:13,625 --> 00:11:15,958
每用一次就会出现裂痕一道
A crack will arise after each use

240
00:11:15,958 --> 00:11:18,083
三次之后就要等第二天日出
After 3 times, you'll have to wait till the next day

241
00:11:18,083 --> 00:11:20,583
裂痕自动消失方可再用
when the cracks vanish

242
00:11:20,875 --> 00:11:22,479
嗯　一天三次　太可怜了
A mere 3 times a day, that's pathetic

243
00:11:22,479 --> 00:11:23,667
哎　总比没有好啊
It's better than nothing

244
00:11:23,667 --> 00:11:26,187
这把扇不能改变生死
This fan can't change life and death

245
00:11:26,187 --> 00:11:28,187
不能改变人心意愿
nor manipulate free will

246
00:11:28,187 --> 00:11:30,292
只不过是一些障眼法
It's just a sleight of hand,

247
00:11:30,292 --> 00:11:33,750
不过凡人往往会迷惑于眼前的事物
but laymen are often bewitched by what they see

248
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:36,208
所以足够你应付的
So it would serve you well

249
00:11:36,917 --> 00:11:38,167
谢谢大士
Thank you, Goddess

250
00:11:38,542 --> 00:11:42,292
凡事小心　切记千万不要堕入邪道
Be careful and don't go astray

251
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:45,250
我知道了啦
I understand

252
00:11:45,250 --> 00:11:46,916
大士摆明是帮你啊
Hey… Goddess does care much about you

253
00:11:46,916 --> 00:11:48,375
没有这把扇子你就糟透了
You'd be in deep shit without this fan

254
00:11:48,375 --> 00:11:50,500
是啊⋯
- Yes…    - Go down

255
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:53,250
哎⋯降龙
Hey… Dragon Fighter

256
00:11:53,458 --> 00:11:56,083
哎　你是不是存心整他　他扇子都没有拿
Hey, you kick him down on purpose

257
00:11:56,083 --> 00:11:57,375
你就这样把他踢下去了
He hasn't got the fan yet

258
00:11:57,708 --> 00:11:59,458
玉帝规定是这个时辰
Heavenly Highness has set the deadline

259
00:11:59,542 --> 00:12:01,354
什么玉帝规定啊
Hey, what's Heavenly Highness has ordered?

260
00:12:01,354 --> 00:12:03,542
哎　我问你　你是干什么吃的你　啊
Hey, have you no sense of responsibility?

261
00:12:05,792 --> 00:12:06,958
哎　你在这儿干什么
Hey, what are you doing here?

262
00:12:07,042 --> 00:12:07,812
换班
Change of shift

263
00:12:07,812 --> 00:12:09,479
哎　那好啊　跟我一道把扇子送给降龙
Good! Let's go down and pass the fan to Dragon Fighter

264
00:12:09,479 --> 00:12:11,354
哎　你没有谕令
Hey… you don't have approval, and you have no magical powers in the mortal world

265
00:12:11,354 --> 00:12:12,062
到了下面你又没有法力

266
00:12:12,062 --> 00:12:13,458
凡人根本看不见你啊
Laymen can't see you

267
00:12:13,458 --> 00:12:15,292
所以才让你跟我一块儿下去
That's why I want you to join me

268
00:12:15,292 --> 00:12:16,541
这里除了玉帝之外
Besides Heavenly Highness,

269
00:12:16,541 --> 00:12:18,833
只有你一个人可以随便出入的　哎　走
only you can come and go as you please

270
00:12:18,833 --> 00:12:20,208
哎　不行　犯天条的
No, this is against heavenly rules

271
00:12:20,208 --> 00:12:21,792
哎呀　犯什么天条嘛　去一次嘛
Forget about the rules.

272
00:12:21,792 --> 00:12:23,146
哎呀　犯什么天条嘛　去一次嘛
Just fly once We'll be back soon. Let's go.

273
00:12:23,146 --> 00:12:24,000
很快就回来的　走啊

274
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:24,875
我不去
I'm not going

275
00:12:25,250 --> 00:12:28,042
降龙煮哮天神犬那天你也吃了
You've eaten the Heavenly Dog cooked by Dragon Fighter that day

276
00:12:29,833 --> 00:12:32,250
王母娘娘的蟠桃你吃了两只
You've had 2 bites of the Queen Mother's peaches too

277
00:12:33,792 --> 00:12:37,271
九天玄女两个婢女洗澡那天
That day while the Ninth Heaven Fairy's maids were taking a bath,

278
00:12:37,271 --> 00:12:38,354
你这个王八蛋　翘起来了
you bastard…

279
00:12:38,354 --> 00:12:39,604
你这个王八蛋　翘起来了
…peeped

280
00:12:39,604 --> 00:12:41,458
别嚷嚷　别嚷嚷嘛
Hey… Stop it! Don't expose it

281
00:12:41,458 --> 00:12:42,687
你是不是犯贱呢
Creep!

282
00:12:42,687 --> 00:12:44,562
一定要把你的丑事翻出来你才肯就范
You won't yield without threats

283
00:12:44,562 --> 00:12:45,396
早去早回
Come back early

284
00:12:45,396 --> 00:12:46,333
怕了嘛
You are sacred, aren't you?

285
00:12:46,333 --> 00:12:48,208
我怕你　我怕你可以了吧
It's not good to let others know

286
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:53,417
(Guo Ching Temple)

287
00:12:54,917 --> 00:12:57,687
左右两边是十八罗汉
The eighteen Lo Hans are on both sides

288
00:12:57,687 --> 00:13:00,125
降龙伏虎在这一边
Dragon and Tiger Fighters are on this side

289
00:13:00,167 --> 00:13:02,958
至于求子嘛⋯就要拜观音大士
To ask for a son,

290
00:13:02,958 --> 00:13:05,750
至于求子嘛⋯就要拜观音大士
you need to pray to Goddess of Mercy

291
00:13:09,083 --> 00:13:11,437
大慈大悲观世音菩萨
Goddess of Mercy,

292
00:13:11,437 --> 00:13:13,750
求你保佑我生下麟儿
do bless me with a son

293
00:13:16,167 --> 00:13:19,708
希望大士真的显灵　要不然的话⋯
Hope Goddess'll show her power, otherwise…

294
00:13:19,708 --> 00:13:22,417
过了今年我可就四十岁了
…I'll be forty next year

295
00:13:22,417 --> 00:13:24,375
我李茂春任节度使多年
I, Li Mau Cheun, have been honest

296
00:13:24,375 --> 00:13:26,208
自认为官清廉　问心无愧
as an envoy all these years

297
00:13:26,208 --> 00:13:28,520
子嗣不需要太强求
With a clear conscience, we don't need to make demands for it

298
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:31,312
老说什么你一清如水　凡事不强求
Yes, just because you are honest,

299
00:13:31,312 --> 00:13:34,292
那上天为什么要我们李家绝后呢
Heaven will not destine us to be without descendants

300
00:13:35,958 --> 00:13:36,875
大师
Master

301
00:13:38,292 --> 00:13:39,167
大师
Master

302
00:13:40,583 --> 00:13:42,270
哎　左右两边是十八罗汉
The eighteen Lo Hans are on both sides

303
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,729
降龙伏虎在这边　如果求子⋯
Dragon and Tiger Fighters on this side

304
00:13:43,729 --> 00:13:44,125
To ask for a son…

305
00:13:44,125 --> 00:13:46,333
大师　你刚才已经说过了
- Master, you said just now    - Goodbye…

306
00:13:46,333 --> 00:13:46,833
啊　再见⋯

307
00:13:46,833 --> 00:13:47,812
我们还没拜神呢
We haven't prayed to the gods yet

308
00:13:47,812 --> 00:13:50,417
哦　拜神⋯
Pray…

309
00:14:07,458 --> 00:14:09,083
降龙罗汉
Dragon Fighter Lo Han?

310
00:14:09,083 --> 00:14:11,208
哎　大师　我们想⋯
Master, we want…

311
00:14:11,542 --> 00:14:13,917
哦　我记得　要儿子嘛
I remember. You want a son, right?

312
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:17,625
没问题
No problem

313
00:14:17,625 --> 00:14:20,354
该不会又怀了十八个月还生不下来吧
Hasn't been a delivery even after 18 months’ pregnancy

314
00:14:20,354 --> 00:14:21,937
夫人　用不着这么担心
Don't worry, madam

315
00:14:21,937 --> 00:14:23,750
老爷、夫人　你们看
Master, madam, look

316
00:14:26,167 --> 00:14:27,250
在哪儿摘的
- Where did you pluck it?    - Over there

317
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:28,333
就在那边摘的
- Where did you pluck it?    - Over there

318
00:14:30,708 --> 00:14:33,625
老爷　怎么会这样呢　老爷　夫人
- Master, why?    - Master, madam

319
00:14:33,875 --> 00:14:35,500
以前显贵诞生就会有灵芝异象出现
Whenever a noble is born,

320
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:36,958
以前显贵诞生就会有灵芝异象出现
Ling Tze plant will appear

321
00:14:36,958 --> 00:14:38,375
但是现在这么看起来的话
From the way things look,

322
00:14:38,375 --> 00:14:39,604
我们这位未出世的少爷一定是贵人呢
our future young master

323
00:14:39,604 --> 00:14:40,937
我们这位未出世的少爷一定是贵人呢
must be a dignitary

324
00:14:40,937 --> 00:14:42,395
现在弄得满屋都是冬菇
The house is now full of mushrooms

325
00:14:42,395 --> 00:14:43,833
夫人　这孩子⋯
Madam, this child…

326
00:14:43,833 --> 00:14:46,875
你自己跟他说吧　他就快要出来了
Tell him yourself, he's coming out

327
00:14:51,917 --> 00:14:54,000
恭喜老爷　夫人生了
Congratulations, master! Madam has given birth

328
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:54,771
男的还是女的
A son or a daughter?

329
00:14:54,771 --> 00:14:58,292
是少爷　恭喜老爷⋯
- A son! Congratulations, master    - Congratulations, master…

330
00:15:01,542 --> 00:15:03,583
哎　怎么会掉到这里来呀
Hey… why have we landed here?

331
00:15:03,583 --> 00:15:04,792
这是什么地方啊
What's this place?

332
00:15:04,792 --> 00:15:05,645
大街
The main street

333
00:15:05,645 --> 00:15:07,917
大街　去你妈的大街
Main street? Damn you

334
00:15:07,917 --> 00:15:10,167
我叫你带我去降龙投胎那个地方
I asked you to take me to Dragon Fighter's birthplace

335
00:15:10,167 --> 00:15:11,708
多走几条街就到了嘛
Just a few streets further

336
00:15:11,708 --> 00:15:13,000
这样也会降落错
How could you land in the wrong place

337
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,708
谁让你刚晃来晃去的
Who asked you to rock so much

338
00:15:14,917 --> 00:15:15,875
儿子究竟上哪儿去了
Where's our son?

339
00:15:15,875 --> 00:15:16,770
儿子究竟上哪儿去了
I don't know either

340
00:15:16,770 --> 00:15:18,854
我也不知道啊
Aiya… damn… it's really painful… really…

341
00:15:18,854 --> 00:15:22,895
天杀的　他妈的　那家馆子吃完了之后
Damn, everyone got diarrhea

342
00:15:22,895 --> 00:15:25,146
每一个人都拉肚子
after eating at that restaurant

343
00:15:25,146 --> 00:15:27,187
就是⋯
- Damn it    - Damn it

344
00:15:27,187 --> 00:15:28,625
麻烦一下　茅房借用一下　十万火急
Could we please use your manure pit?

345
00:15:28,625 --> 00:15:30,354
麻烦一下　茅房借用一下　十万火急
- It's urgent    - Yes…

346
00:15:30,354 --> 00:15:31,333
我们只有两间茅房　请便吧
We only have two

347
00:15:31,333 --> 00:15:32,333
我们只有两间茅房　请便吧
Help yourself

348
00:15:32,333 --> 00:15:34,125
I can't hold on

349
00:15:34,125 --> 00:15:35,792
他们俩跑得还真快啊
- So graceless    - They run so swiftly

350
00:15:35,792 --> 00:15:37,292
我快憋不住了
I can hardly hold on

351
00:15:37,875 --> 00:15:38,875
So this is the right place?

352
00:15:38,875 --> 00:15:41,416
哎　降龙⋯
Dragon Fighter

353
00:15:41,416 --> 00:15:43,604
哇　老兄　我等你好久了
Brother, I waited for ages, brother

354
00:15:43,604 --> 00:15:44,916
哎　不关我的事
Not my fault!

355
00:15:44,916 --> 00:15:47,187
哎　是麒麟怪带着我东跑西跑的
This bastard misled me

356
00:15:47,187 --> 00:15:48,625
哎　别说那么多了　快点拿回你的扇子
Never mind, take your fan, here…

357
00:15:48,625 --> 00:15:50,708
哇　我叫你买两只蟋蟀
- Quick and give them to me    - Hey… Lung…

358
00:15:50,708 --> 00:15:51,979
你怎么去这么久啊
What took you ages to buy 2 crickets?

359
00:15:51,979 --> 00:15:54,020
哎　我是精挑细选选两只
- I hand-picked two that fight best    - Brag

360
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:56,958
哎　阿龙　糟糕　他根本看不见我
Lung… Oh God! He can't see me

361
00:15:56,958 --> 00:15:57,854
他已经是个凡人了　你想跟他接触
He is a layman now.

362
00:15:57,854 --> 00:15:58,833
他已经是个凡人了　你想跟他接触
To contact him,

363
00:15:58,833 --> 00:16:00,292
就要投胎转世变成肉身
you must re-incarnate and become human

364
00:16:00,292 --> 00:16:02,333
他已经长这么大了　投胎也来不及了
He's now grown; too late for re-incarnation I guess

365
00:16:02,333 --> 00:16:04,000
上面一天　凡间就十年
A day in Heaven is ten years in the mortal world

366
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,417
但是别怕　我会把你吹大的
Don't worry! I'll blow you up

367
00:16:05,417 --> 00:16:06,541
嗯　吹大
Blow me up?

368
00:16:06,541 --> 00:16:07,500
不过你会失去法力哦
But you'll lose your magic powers

369
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:08,229
不过你会失去法力哦
