爸爸⋯

563
00:23:47,208 --> 00:23:51,583
摸摸⋯

564
00:23:58,542 --> 00:24:01,271
摸摸

565
00:24:01,271 --> 00:24:02,625
就是这里了
It's here

566
00:24:13,167 --> 00:24:15,312
哎　老兄　我等你好久了
Brother, I waited for you for a long time

567
00:24:15,312 --> 00:24:16,292
你是哪位
Who are you, sir?

568
00:24:16,292 --> 00:24:18,729
土地公啊　这也不能怪你
God of Earth

569
00:24:18,729 --> 00:24:20,750
你的元神还没有回来
I don't blame you. Your Yun San (spirit) has not returned

570
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,646
你不要怕
Don't be frightened! You'll be fine once you get back your golden body

571
00:24:22,646 --> 00:24:24,167
只要你把金身拿回来就没事了
Don't be frightened! You'll be fine once you get back your golden body

572
00:24:24,167 --> 00:24:26,208
还有啊　你这个金身呢
Also, your golden body…

573
00:24:26,208 --> 00:24:28,958
官府跟强盗都争着要呢
…is sought by both bureaucracy and the underworld

574
00:24:28,958 --> 00:24:31,333
上个月那一次来争的人可多着呢
Most people came last month

575
00:24:31,750 --> 00:24:33,375
你到底是土地公还是老大
Are you God of Earth or local mob?

576
00:24:39,458 --> 00:24:41,208
金身就在这里
The golden body is here

577
00:24:50,792 --> 00:24:52,396
金身就是我　我也⋯
Totally understand! The golden body is me and I am the golden body

578
00:24:52,396 --> 00:24:54,542
你跟我说没用　跟他们说去
No point telling me, tell them instead

579
00:24:54,542 --> 00:24:55,333
哎　对
Yes

580
00:24:55,333 --> 00:24:57,375
哎⋯你们两个头放错了
Your heads have been exchanged

581
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,791
不会吧　先换过来
Really?

582
00:24:58,791 --> 00:25:00,083
不会吧　先换过来
Change back first

583
00:25:04,833 --> 00:25:05,729
什么东西
What is it?

584
00:25:05,729 --> 00:25:06,687
木鱼
A wooden fish

585
00:25:06,687 --> 00:25:07,792
鱼
Fish

586
00:25:10,417 --> 00:25:12,646
啊　这也能吃啊
Is this possible?

587
00:25:12,646 --> 00:25:14,979
哎　师傅　打搅你一会儿　容我说两句话
Please spare some time and listen to me

588
00:25:14,979 --> 00:25:15,604
我不认识你
I don't know you

589
00:25:15,604 --> 00:25:16,375
在十三世之前
Thirteenth life cycles ago,

590
00:25:16,375 --> 00:25:17,687
我在这间寺庙当和尚
I was a monk in this temple

591
00:25:17,687 --> 00:25:19,833
到了八世上下我就做了住持了
Then by the eighth life cycles, I became an abbot

592
00:25:19,833 --> 00:25:22,333
也就是这个金身还没有圆寂之前
I was the golden body right there The Sing Ging Abbot before he passed away

593
00:25:22,333 --> 00:25:24,479
性经大师然后升了天做了神了
I then ascended to Heaven and became a fairy Follow me

594
00:25:24,479 --> 00:25:25,833
请跟我来　然后你猜会怎么样
Guess what happened afterwards?

595
00:25:25,833 --> 00:25:27,083
最后就变成一个降龙罗汉
The fairy became Dragon Fighter Lo Han

596
00:25:27,083 --> 00:25:28,541
最后就变成一个降龙罗汉
That's me

597
00:25:28,541 --> 00:25:29,375
也就是我本人
Follow me

598
00:25:29,375 --> 00:25:30,896
这次我下来是办点小事情
I came down on a mission

599
00:25:30,896 --> 00:25:32,375
至于什么事情你就不用管了
As regards what the mission is, you need not know

600
00:25:32,375 --> 00:25:34,375
看你这个德行　资质平常
You are at best a common person

601
00:25:34,375 --> 00:25:35,896
念你在寺里待那么久了
However, considering the length of your service,

602
00:25:35,896 --> 00:25:37,541
没有功劳也有苦劳
you've accumulated some worthiness so I'll give you some face…

603
00:25:37,541 --> 00:25:39,104
在你徒弟面前我就叫你一声师傅
…and address you as master in front of your pupils

604
00:25:39,104 --> 00:25:40,958
够意思吧
…and address you as master in front of your pupils

605
00:25:40,958 --> 00:25:42,000
还不赶快去拿件衣服给我换去
Should show you due respect

606
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,083
还不赶快去拿件衣服给我换去
Go get me some clothes to change

607
00:25:43,250 --> 00:25:44,646
师傅　他是疯子
Master, he is mad

608
00:25:44,646 --> 00:25:45,875
可是我一看到他我就很欣赏他
So am I

609
00:25:45,875 --> 00:25:47,083
可是我一看到他我就很欣赏他
I admire him on sight.

610
00:25:47,083 --> 00:25:47,875
拿衣服来
- Bring me the clothes    - Yes

611
00:25:47,875 --> 00:25:48,708
是
- Bring me the clothes    - Yes

612
00:25:51,833 --> 00:25:52,833
乖　哈
You're lovely

613
00:25:55,333 --> 00:25:57,625
哇　你怎么那么快就吃光了
You've eaten all of it so quickly?

614
00:25:57,625 --> 00:25:59,417
外面还有一个更大的呢
There's a bigger one outside

615
00:26:01,583 --> 00:26:04,208
这一根是我的宝贝　不能吃的
This is made of steel and can't be eaten

616
00:26:04,250 --> 00:26:05,917
要吃吃后面那个
Eat the drum behind

617
00:26:06,167 --> 00:26:08,250
求你温柔一点　拜托
I beg you not to bite, please

618
00:26:08,792 --> 00:26:10,229
师傅　照惯例帮我取个名吧
Master

619
00:26:10,229 --> 00:26:11,667
师傅　照惯例帮我取个名吧
Give me a priest name as in the normal procedure

620
00:26:11,667 --> 00:26:13,375
你这么癫　就叫济癫吧
You are so mad, I'll call you Mad Monk

621
00:26:13,625 --> 00:26:14,625
非常好
Very good

622
00:26:16,125 --> 00:26:21,666
救命啊　不要追我
Help! Don't chase me…

623
00:26:21,666 --> 00:26:22,750
九世乞丐
A beggar for 9 lives?

624
00:26:23,333 --> 00:26:25,917
不要啊
Don't

625
00:26:26,042 --> 00:26:30,083
真的好苦啊
Horrible! Really horrible

626
00:26:30,083 --> 00:26:31,708
啊　袁霸天　快躲
What? Yun Ba Tin

627
00:26:31,708 --> 00:26:33,333
啊　袁霸天　快躲
Hide quickly

628
00:26:35,625 --> 00:26:37,521
袁霸天来了　先到我家躲一躲　走
Hey, Yun is here!

629
00:26:37,521 --> 00:26:39,417
袁霸天来了　先到我家躲一躲　走
Hide in my home, quick

630
00:26:39,583 --> 00:26:40,667
土地公
Hey, God of Earth

631
00:26:44,667 --> 00:26:46,354
九世恶人　全都到齐了
A villain of 9 lives?

632
00:26:46,354 --> 00:26:48,042
九世恶人　全都到齐了
Save my time

633
00:26:51,750 --> 00:26:53,521
救命啊
Help

634
00:26:53,521 --> 00:26:55,458
我早说不要让我再看到你
I told you not to let me see you

635
00:26:55,875 --> 00:26:59,167
我一看到你　我就火大
A mere sight of you makes me so mad

636
00:26:59,250 --> 00:27:01,458
我也不想让你看到我　你不要过来
I don't want you to see me either. Keep away

637
00:27:01,458 --> 00:27:03,708
我要避开你　但是避不了
I wanted to avoid you, but couldn't

638
00:27:03,708 --> 00:27:05,229
You can hit my head,

639
00:27:05,229 --> 00:27:07,250
你打我的头好了　不要打我的背啊
not the back

640
00:27:15,292 --> 00:27:16,646
好　我把庙也烧了　看你能往哪儿跑
Run? I'll burn down the temple,

641
00:27:16,646 --> 00:27:17,937
好　我把庙也烧了　看你能往哪儿跑
see if you can get away

642
00:27:17,937 --> 00:27:19,417
连你这个臭和尚也烧掉
I'll burn you, stinky monk, too

643
00:27:23,833 --> 00:27:26,667
我要烧你　你竟敢吹灭我的火
I want to burn you, how dare you blow out my fire?

644
00:27:47,333 --> 00:27:49,792
你⋯
You…

645
00:27:53,583 --> 00:27:54,625
痛吧
Does it hurt?

646
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:57,292
我只是让你了解被人欺负的痛苦
Now you know the agony of being bullied

647
00:27:57,750 --> 00:28:00,167
放下屠刀　立地成佛
Lay down the sword and be a Buddha

648
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:03,666
我不会生气　我疼你　我爱你
Don't be mad! Give you a kiss

649
00:28:03,666 --> 00:28:05,104
重新做人　乖孩子
Take my advice and be a new person

650
00:28:05,104 --> 00:28:06,958
重新做人　乖孩子
Good boy

651
00:28:11,417 --> 00:28:15,333
不可能　我的娘哎
Impossible…

652
00:28:19,542 --> 00:28:21,083
回去上个厕所想清楚
Think over indoors.

653
00:28:21,083 --> 00:28:22,458
我会很快回来找你的
I'll come to you soon

654
00:28:26,042 --> 00:28:27,917
你不要再行乞了　跟我回家吧
Don't be a beggar anymore. Go home with me

655
00:28:27,917 --> 00:28:30,708
我不要⋯
What a horrible monster

656
00:28:30,708 --> 00:28:31,875
你怕什么
What are you afraid of?

657
00:28:31,875 --> 00:28:33,167
我不去啊
No, I'm not going

658
00:28:33,333 --> 00:28:34,542
走了
Get going

659
00:28:37,042 --> 00:28:39,208
哥哥⋯

660
00:28:40,375 --> 00:28:43,771
啊　哥哥⋯
Brother. Milk… Brother. Milk.

661
00:28:43,771 --> 00:28:47,167
啊　哥哥⋯
Brother. Milk… Brother. Milk.

662
00:28:47,333 --> 00:28:49,896
孩子　你怎么弄成这个样子　爸爸
- Son, what happened to you?    - Bakbak

663
00:28:49,896 --> 00:28:52,208
嚯　我换了发型　不错吧
I changed my hairstyle. Not bad, right?

664
00:28:52,208 --> 00:28:54,333
啊　房子怎么也变了样了
What happened to the house?

665
00:28:55,792 --> 00:28:56,833
(Li Sau Yun, I vow to kill your whole family)

666
00:28:56,833 --> 00:28:57,917
(Signed by Yun Ba Tin)

667
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:01,354
修缘呢　你怎么会惹上袁霸天这种人呢
Sau Yun, why mess with a character like Yun Ba Tin?

668
00:29:01,354 --> 00:29:02,500
屙巴巴⋯
Bakbak

669
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:03,667
屙巴巴⋯
Clean white, white

670
00:29:03,667 --> 00:29:06,292
李修缘　我誓要杀你全家
Li Sau Yun, I vow to kill your whole family

671
00:29:06,292 --> 00:29:07,458
袁霸天留字
Signed by Yun Ba Tin

672
00:29:07,458 --> 00:29:09,500
哎　老爷　他杀光了我们全家的畜牲
Master…, they killed all the poultries,

673
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:10,875
连蟑螂老鼠都没放过
even rats and roaches

674
00:29:10,875 --> 00:29:13,104
还有只蟑螂是大肚子的　太残忍了
Also includes a pregnant roach, so cruel

675
00:29:13,104 --> 00:29:15,250
哎呀　还好我们跟老爷夫人去拜神了
Luckily you went to the temple with master and madam

676
00:29:15,250 --> 00:29:17,167
这么快就查到我底细　真厉害
Found out my background so soon. Great!

677
00:29:17,167 --> 00:29:19,083
可惜我已经不是李修缘了
Unfortunately I'm not Li Sau Yun anymore

678
00:29:19,083 --> 00:29:21,417
嘿　看不出来他还写了一手好书法
His calligraphy is good, couldn't tell from appearance

679
00:29:21,417 --> 00:29:23,187
连日子都写下了
He even put down the date,

680
00:29:23,187 --> 00:29:25,562
耶嘿　这个家伙做事还挺有条理的
such an organized person

681
00:29:25,562 --> 00:29:27,708
哎呀　家里被人弄成这个样子
Son, look at the mess here,

682
00:29:27,708 --> 00:29:29,167
你还说这些话
yet you're still concerned with such matters

683
00:29:29,958 --> 00:29:35,000
啊　老爷⋯
Master…

684
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:36,833
你爸爸他不行了
Your dad won't make it

685
00:29:37,500 --> 00:29:41,396
哇　寿终正寝　福气到极点了
Natural death is his good fortune. Let me see,

686
00:29:41,396 --> 00:29:42,958
让我算算　哎哟　下辈子做皇帝啊
he'll be an emperor in his next life. Good for him

687
00:29:42,958 --> 00:29:44,917
已经很不错了
he'll be an emperor in his next life. Good for him

688
00:29:45,083 --> 00:29:47,646
修缘呢　你这孩子　你是不是疯了
Sau Yun…, are you crazy?

689
00:29:47,646 --> 00:29:49,958
对了　现在我的新名字叫济癫
Bingo, my new name is Mad Monk

690
00:29:49,958 --> 00:29:52,875
啊　哎呀　天呢

691
00:29:52,875 --> 00:29:57,229
我们李家是做错了什么事了呀
Heaven, what has our family done wrong?

692
00:29:57,229 --> 00:29:59,187
是啊　你要是没做错事
Yes, if you've done nothing wrong,

693
00:29:59,187 --> 00:30:01,375
我还应该跟他一块儿死才对呀
you should die with him

694
00:30:02,708 --> 00:30:05,250
啊　夫人⋯
Madam…

695
00:30:05,250 --> 00:30:07,354
哎　快拿麝香让夫人闻一闻呢　快
Give her some musk to smell, hurry

696
00:30:07,354 --> 00:30:08,729
哎　别动　他们俩好好的
Don't move

697
00:30:08,729 --> 00:30:10,021
你们就不要多事
Master and madam are fine, you shouldn't fiddle

698
00:30:10,021 --> 00:30:11,354
他们俩是鸳鸯蝴蝶命　死也死一双啊
They're destined to become butterfly lovers,

699
00:30:11,354 --> 00:30:12,646
他们俩是鸳鸯蝴蝶命　死也死一双啊
and they always die together

700
00:30:12,646 --> 00:30:14,958
他们俩在下一辈子将会再续未了情
They'll continue their romance in the next life

701
00:30:14,958 --> 00:30:17,291
真是羡煞旁人呢
How admirable

702
00:30:17,291 --> 00:30:19,416
哎　少爷　那我们该怎么办呢
Young master, what should we do then?

703
00:30:19,416 --> 00:30:21,604
这是喜事　赶快买一只鸡回来庆贺一下
It's an auspicious affair, get a chicken to celebrate

704
00:30:21,604 --> 00:30:23,708
还有你　找个仵作回来送他们一程
And you, get an undertaker to give them a lift

705
00:30:23,708 --> 00:30:25,708
走吧⋯快点⋯
Go… Hurry…

706
00:30:25,708 --> 00:30:26,958
我们快走吧
Let's go quickly

707
00:30:27,417 --> 00:30:28,979
哎　你还不可以走
- You can't go yet    - What?

708
00:30:28,979 --> 00:30:30,542
啊
- You can't go yet    - What?

709
00:30:30,542 --> 00:30:32,542
哎　睡一会儿倒可以
But you can sleep for a while

710
00:30:32,542 --> 00:30:34,042
我⋯

711
00:30:34,583 --> 00:30:35,542
Aiya…

712
00:30:36,667 --> 00:30:44,333
扇扇⋯
Fan…

713
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,333
鸭乖乖⋯
Good duckling… You two've lots of kids,

714
00:30:49,333 --> 00:30:50,875
你们夫妻俩生了这么多
Good duckling… You two've lots of kids,

715
00:30:50,875 --> 00:30:51,937
送一只给我吃
why not give me one to fill my stomach

716
00:30:51,937 --> 00:30:52,792
如果我数到三
why not give me one to fill my stomach

717
00:30:52,792 --> 00:30:54,687
你们没有摇头那就表示答应了
If you don't shake your head when I count to 3,

718
00:30:54,687 --> 00:30:55,229
一　二　三
that means you consent

719
00:30:55,229 --> 00:30:55,917
一　二　三
1, 2, 3

720
00:30:57,125 --> 00:30:58,542
鸭子
- Aiya    - Outrageous

721
00:30:59,042 --> 00:31:00,062
又是你
You again?

722
00:31:00,062 --> 00:31:00,958
岂有此理
Sunk deep to a duck thief?

723
00:31:00,958 --> 00:31:03,583
不要过来⋯
You keep away! Keep away…

724
00:31:03,875 --> 00:31:05,229
我问过它们夫妻俩了
I got the couple's consent

725
00:31:05,229 --> 00:31:06,292
你问过它们
Did you ask?

726
00:31:06,708 --> 00:31:07,833
它们问过你吗
Did he ask you?

727
00:31:07,833 --> 00:31:09,167
没有　没有
No…

728
00:31:09,458 --> 00:31:11,396
啊　鸭子怎么会说话
What? Ducks can speak too?

729
00:31:11,396 --> 00:31:12,667
你还有什么话说
What more do you have to say?

730
00:31:13,083 --> 00:31:15,521
你不要再拉我了
Stop pulling me…

731
00:31:15,521 --> 00:31:16,687
一定是它妈妈勾引那只九官鸟
His mother must've seduced a parrot that's why he could speak

732
00:31:16,687 --> 00:31:17,875
它才会说话
His mother must've seduced a parrot that's why he could speak

733
00:31:18,083 --> 00:31:19,875
哎　对了　一定是勾引了九官鸟
His mother has seduced a parrot?

734
00:31:19,875 --> 00:31:21,646
人家的妈妈勾引什么人是它的事
That's totally up to his mother

735
00:31:21,646 --> 00:31:24,271
什么时候要你来管　我告诉你
Who asked you to meddle in it? I tell you,

736
00:31:24,271 --> 00:31:27,458
我们做人处世一定要有点自尊
we must have self-respect as a human

737
00:31:27,917 --> 00:31:29,396
既然你想吃它们
If you want to eat them, you must get their consent first

738
00:31:29,396 --> 00:31:30,875
得先得到它们同意啊
If you want to eat them, you must get their consent first

739
00:31:30,958 --> 00:31:32,521
哪有人情愿被别人吃的
Who would consent to being eaten?

740
00:31:32,521 --> 00:31:33,458
他妈的
Damn

741
00:31:33,708 --> 00:31:35,479
我现在想吃你们
I want to eat you now Whoever's willing can come with me

742
00:31:35,479 --> 00:31:37,250
哪个愿意的　可以跟我走　哼
I want to eat you now Whoever's willing can come with me

743
00:31:49,625 --> 00:31:53,958
哎哟　我⋯我崇拜你啊
So great

744
00:31:54,375 --> 00:31:55,875
可以叫我一声师傅了吧
Worth to greet me as Master?

745
00:31:56,792 --> 00:31:58,896
师傅　有什么我可以效劳的
Master, what can I do for you? Just let me know

746
00:31:58,896 --> 00:32:01,000
请尽管吩咐
Master, what can I do for you? Just let me know

747
00:32:01,083 --> 00:32:02,604
晚了　你该睡了
It's late, you should sleep

748
00:32:02,604 --> 00:32:05,250
啊　师傅　你怎么把我当猪
Master, I am like a pig. I only sleep in daylight

