00:38:49,333 --> 00:38:51,541
啊⋯送死⋯到哪儿去找⋯
Where to find one…

937
00:38:51,541 --> 00:38:53,042
哎　怡香院里多的是
You can find many at Yi Heung Brothel

938
00:38:53,042 --> 00:38:53,667
Yes…

939
00:38:53,667 --> 00:38:57,458
Let's go…

940
00:38:57,500 --> 00:38:59,958
啊　哎　老鸨
Boss

941
00:39:02,042 --> 00:39:03,437
哟　这班臭男人怎么这么早就来了
- Those lousy men come so early?    - Yes…

942
00:39:03,437 --> 00:39:04,833
就是
- Those lousy men come so early?    - Yes…

943
00:39:04,833 --> 00:39:07,270
快⋯叫她们交出一个人来　啊　快点⋯
- What if they won't agree?    - Go in…

944
00:39:07,270 --> 00:39:09,520
如果她们不肯交人那怎么办呢
- What if they won't agree?    - Go in…

945
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:10,854
哎　这关乎全城人的安危
This concerns the safety of the whole city, they have no choice

946
00:39:10,854 --> 00:39:12,271
由不得她们不肯了
This concerns the safety of the whole city, they have no choice

947
00:39:12,271 --> 00:39:15,042
大家一起进去　地保　你先走啊　快⋯
Let's go in together. Chief, you go first

948
00:39:19,875 --> 00:39:22,250
什么事
- What happened?    - Go…

949
00:39:22,250 --> 00:39:22,667
停

950
00:39:22,667 --> 00:39:25,583
你们搞什么鬼啊
Freeze! What's the matter?

951
00:39:26,625 --> 00:39:28,333
天爷　你也知道

952
00:39:28,333 --> 00:39:30,271
这次瘟疫死了那么多的人
Master Tin, you know, the plague has killed a lot of people

953
00:39:30,271 --> 00:39:31,458
关我怡香院什么事
What has it to do with my Yi Heung Brothel?

954
00:39:31,458 --> 00:39:34,208
他们说随便找几个姑娘去祭神
They want to get some girls as sacrifices

955
00:39:34,208 --> 00:39:35,458
干吗不找你妈去祭呀
Why don't you send your mother?

956
00:39:35,458 --> 00:39:35,917
是啊

957
00:39:35,917 --> 00:39:38,104
昨天你不是告诉我很讨厌你老婆
That's right You told me you hated your wife last night

958
00:39:38,104 --> 00:39:39,167
叫她去呀
Why don't you send her?

959
00:39:39,167 --> 00:39:40,937
哎　天爷　你很为难　嚯
Master Tin, I know it's a hard decision for you

960
00:39:40,937 --> 00:39:42,979
我有什么为难的　这里全是我的人
Why? They are all mine

961
00:39:42,979 --> 00:39:45,000
要她死就死　要生就生　对不对
Their lives are in my hands

962
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:45,312
Right?

963
00:39:45,312 --> 00:39:46,541
哎　对
That's right…

964
00:39:46,541 --> 00:39:47,875
啊　哪几个没人要的　统统给我站出来
Take those ones who nobody wants

965
00:39:47,875 --> 00:39:49,750
我可以省点米饭
Take those ones who nobody wants

966
00:39:49,750 --> 00:39:52,292
站出来　快⋯快点　站出来
I can save some costs

967
00:39:52,292 --> 00:39:54,187
哎　用不了那么多　一个半个就够了
No need for so many, one is more than enough

968
00:39:54,187 --> 00:39:57,875
哎　出来围一圈　围一圈⋯快点⋯
- Come and form a circle…    - So bad…

969
00:39:57,875 --> 00:40:02,000
围好⋯围个圈啊　快点⋯围好了⋯
- Hurry… Quick! Come…    - Outrageous…

970
00:40:02,625 --> 00:40:03,270
驼子躺下

971
00:40:03,270 --> 00:40:04,542
哎　好
Hunchback, lie down

972
00:40:10,042 --> 00:40:11,875
他的脚趾向谁就是谁了
Whoever his toe points to, will be the one

973
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:16,458
- Turn…    - So scary…

974
00:40:30,167 --> 00:40:32,875
哦　你耍赖
You're cheating

975
00:40:33,875 --> 00:40:36,166
哦⋯你⋯不是我⋯
Not me…

976
00:40:36,166 --> 00:40:38,395
哦⋯你⋯不是我⋯
Take her away

977
00:40:38,395 --> 00:40:40,208
走⋯拉到祭坛去⋯走⋯
Not me! You've seen it

978
00:40:40,208 --> 00:40:41,479
哎　你记不记得你昨天跟我说过什么
- Get going    - Take her away

979
00:40:41,479 --> 00:40:43,000
哎　你记不记得你昨天跟我说过什么
Remember what you said to me yesterday?

980
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:44,646
我说你收费太高啊　走⋯
I said you charged a high price. Move

981
00:40:44,646 --> 00:40:46,292
我说你收费太高啊　走⋯
Cut the crap, take her away

982
00:40:46,333 --> 00:40:47,167
不是我

983
00:40:47,417 --> 00:40:50,250
嗯　敢在我怡香院撒野　嗯
You dare create trouble here?

984
00:40:51,042 --> 00:40:56,583
不⋯不是我
No! No… Not me…

985
00:40:56,583 --> 00:40:58,604
怎么祭
Hey, how should the sacrifice be offered?

986
00:40:58,604 --> 00:40:59,416
哎　红烧
Braise

987
00:40:59,416 --> 00:41:01,833
给我留点时间
- It'll take a long time then    - Not me…

988
00:41:01,833 --> 00:41:02,937
你们先等着　留只左腿给我
Leave the left leg for me I'll take a rest

989
00:41:02,937 --> 00:41:04,292
我先歇会儿
Leave the left leg for me I'll take a rest

990
00:41:04,625 --> 00:41:06,792
抓她去沐浴更衣　走
Clean her up and get changed. Go

991
00:41:06,875 --> 00:41:08,375
不要啊
No…

992
00:41:20,958 --> 00:41:24,167
哇　好漂亮　烧死了多可惜
She's so beautiful. What a waste to burn her?

993
00:41:24,792 --> 00:41:26,292
赶快想办法救她
Find a way to save her

994
00:41:26,833 --> 00:41:28,020
漂亮的才救　烧你就不用救了
To help only the pretty one?

995
00:41:28,020 --> 00:41:29,208
漂亮的才救　烧你就不用救了
If so, I won't save you then

996
00:41:33,167 --> 00:41:34,542
哎　你这把扇子
Your… your fan has to wait until dawn for its power to return?

997
00:41:34,542 --> 00:41:35,917
真的要等到天亮了才能变东西啊
Your… your fan has to wait until dawn for its power to return?

998
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:37,729
与其等到天亮
Rather than wait until dawn,

999
00:41:37,729 --> 00:41:39,583
倒不如等我的法力消失好了
better off to wait till my powers are gone

1000
00:41:39,750 --> 00:41:40,875
喂　我解释给你听你就会明白了
Go

1001
00:41:40,875 --> 00:41:41,958
喂　我解释给你听你就会明白了
You'll understand once I explain to you

1002
00:41:41,958 --> 00:41:44,458
不明白　我就是不明白
No need. I don't understand anyway

1003
00:41:44,458 --> 00:41:46,062
我⋯照我吩咐做　烧啊⋯
Just do as I say

1004
00:41:46,062 --> 00:41:47,625
吉时已到
The auspicious time has come

1005
00:41:50,583 --> 00:41:52,333
哎　慢一点　请问一下
Wait! How you know that

1006
00:41:52,333 --> 00:41:54,854
你怎么知道烧死了她就会没有瘟疫呢
burning her will stop the plague?

1007
00:41:54,854 --> 00:41:59,083
哎⋯玉帝托梦告诉我的
- Heavenly Highness told me in a dream    - Oh…

1008
00:42:02,458 --> 00:42:07,208
王母娘娘刚刚托梦告诉我
Queen Mother told me to burn…

1009
00:42:08,917 --> 00:42:11,042
说烧你娘呀
- …your mother in a dream    - It can't be…

1010
00:42:11,042 --> 00:42:13,167
啊　你⋯
- …your mother in a dream    - It can't be…

1011
00:42:13,667 --> 00:42:15,979
还说要连骂三次
And if I scold you three times,

1012
00:42:15,979 --> 00:42:19,708
你脸上那两块黑痣就会没有了
the two moles on your face will disappear

1013
00:42:19,708 --> 00:42:21,250
神经病　走开
You are crazy, go away

1014
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,750
时间到了　快骂
It's time, scold him

1015
00:42:22,958 --> 00:42:24,208
我⋯我不要
I dare not

1016
00:42:25,833 --> 00:42:26,750
烧啊⋯

1017
00:42:26,750 --> 00:42:29,333
〝离〞你⋯我〝离〞你
Bastard, bastard, bastard

1018
00:42:30,917 --> 00:42:34,833
啊⋯不见了⋯好灵啊⋯是啊⋯
It really works…

1019
00:42:34,833 --> 00:42:37,521
你们看他的脸　比神仙还要灵验
Look at his face, more divine than god

1020
00:42:37,521 --> 00:42:40,083
哎　各位　他已经跟王母娘娘谈好了
Everyone, he has made an agreement with Queen Mother,

1021
00:42:40,083 --> 00:42:42,375
以后不会再有瘟疫了　马上放人
there'll be no more plague

1022
00:42:42,375 --> 00:42:43,125
Release her now

1023
00:42:43,708 --> 00:42:45,958
如果放了她　还有瘟疫那怎么办呢
What if there'll be plague again after she is released?

1024
00:42:45,958 --> 00:42:48,146
对啊⋯还有瘟疫怎么办⋯怎么办⋯
Right…

1025
00:42:48,146 --> 00:42:50,167
对啊⋯还有瘟疫怎么办⋯怎么办⋯
What to do? Tell me…

1026
00:42:50,167 --> 00:42:52,875
我不知道⋯不知道啊
None of my business! Don't! I don't know

1027
00:42:53,833 --> 00:42:54,750
哎　这样子了
Can't release her

1028
00:42:54,750 --> 00:42:56,708
要是烧死她还有瘟疫的话　就烧死你们
However, if the plague still persists after she's burnt to death

1029
00:42:56,708 --> 00:42:58,917
要是烧死她还有瘟疫的话　就烧死你们
I'll burn you all

1030
00:42:59,875 --> 00:43:03,458
哎⋯听到没有　马上放人
Hear that? Release her now

1031
00:43:03,458 --> 00:43:05,166
哎　火这么大怎么放啊
The fire is so fierce. How to release?

1032
00:43:05,166 --> 00:43:06,375
拿水来浇熄它
Bring some water to put it out

1033
00:43:06,375 --> 00:43:09,083
街口的井给封了　哪来的水呀
The well nearby is blocked. Where can we find water?

1034
00:43:10,333 --> 00:43:13,125
没有水　随便什么水都可以
Any kind of water will do

1035
00:43:13,250 --> 00:43:14,792
哦　我明白了
Got it

1036
00:43:20,375 --> 00:43:23,520
嗯　你实在太神勇了　避都不避啊
You're so bold, you don't even flinch

1037
00:43:23,520 --> 00:43:25,542
口水嘛　又不是没吃过
It's just saliva, no need to be scared

1038
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:13,083
谢谢你
Thank you

1039
00:44:14,333 --> 00:44:15,750
不客气
My pleasure

1040
00:44:16,583 --> 00:44:18,500
I…

1041
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,292
你休息一下
Take a rest

1042
00:44:36,292 --> 00:44:39,500
哎　你不要走
Don't go

1043
00:44:40,208 --> 00:44:43,958
你放心　那些人不会再来烧你了
Don't worry, they won't burn you again

1044
00:44:44,208 --> 00:44:46,750
那些臭男人平时在床上都对我那么好
Those lousy men were nice to me when in bed

1045
00:44:46,917 --> 00:44:49,542
他们干吗要放火来烧我
Why did they want to burn me to death?

1046
00:44:49,750 --> 00:44:51,750
原因是这样子的
It's simple Those men who come to you,

1047
00:44:51,750 --> 00:44:53,104
那些人来找你　就跟坐马桶一样
It's simple Those men who come to you,

1048
00:44:53,104 --> 00:44:54,042
treat you like a shit-bowl

1049
00:44:54,042 --> 00:44:56,833
坐的时候固然是很舒坦
They feel comfortable when sitting on it,

1050
00:44:56,833 --> 00:44:59,875
但是绝对不会对马桶有感情的
but they're not emotionally tied to it

1051
00:45:00,417 --> 00:45:01,791
我不明白
What do you mean?

1052
00:45:01,791 --> 00:45:03,687
也就是说　请你以后不要再做马桶了
That is… to say, never be a shit-bowl anymore Get it?

1053
00:45:03,687 --> 00:45:05,625
明白吗
That is… to say, never be a shit-bowl anymore Get it?

1054
00:45:05,917 --> 00:45:07,042
我明白了
Yes

1055
00:45:08,250 --> 00:45:09,458
你干什么
What are you doing?

1056
00:45:09,458 --> 00:45:10,562
我要报答你呀
I want to repay you

1057
00:45:10,562 --> 00:45:13,417
哎　不要　你真是〝鸡〞性难改耶
Don't! Your whorish nature is incorrigible

1058
00:45:13,417 --> 00:45:14,729
我不收你钱的呀
It's free

1059
00:45:14,729 --> 00:45:15,917
你不收钱　我还收呢
Big brother, you don't charge,

1060
00:45:15,917 --> 00:45:17,146
你不收钱　我还收呢
but I do

1061
00:45:17,146 --> 00:45:18,167
你连马桶都不如
Worse than a shit-bowl

1062
00:45:18,333 --> 00:45:19,479
你除了会躺下收钱之外
What else can you do besides lying down for money?

1063
00:45:19,479 --> 00:45:20,625
你还会做什么
What else can you do besides lying down for money?

1064
00:45:23,792 --> 00:45:26,833
嗯　倒挂也行　不会吧
You can do it upside down? No way…

1065
00:45:26,833 --> 00:45:29,208
哎呀　妈的　我怎么会跟你谈这个玩意儿
I don't mean that

1066
00:45:29,208 --> 00:45:31,000
我是说你可不可以换一个职业
What I mean is can you find another job…

1067
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:33,333
譬如说卖卖豆腐也行啊
…like selling bean curd?

1068
00:45:33,792 --> 00:45:35,875
那摊子摆门口还是床边啊
Should I put the stall at the door or beside the bed?

1069
00:45:38,333 --> 00:45:40,375
你⋯

1070
00:45:42,167 --> 00:45:45,458
师傅⋯要到半块豆腐乳
Master… I got half a piece of preserved bean curd

1071
00:45:46,167 --> 00:45:50,125
哇　嗯　好香啊　有没有我的份
Smells good, any for me?

1072
00:45:50,208 --> 00:45:51,708
豆腐乳你自己吃好了
Keep the bean curd for yourself

1073
00:45:52,125 --> 00:45:55,417
哎　别这样　连汤都喝光了
Oh no, finish the sauce too

1074
00:45:56,833 --> 00:45:58,770
是条洋狗　没什么味
It's a foreign dog, not much taste

1075
00:45:58,770 --> 00:46:00,312
还有一口　我试试就知道了
There's one left. Try and I'll know

1076
00:46:00,312 --> 00:46:02,750
哎　这只狗生前咬死了两个人
This dog has bitten two people to death before

1077
00:46:02,750 --> 00:46:04,229
我现在吃它是超度它
Eating it means I'm honoring its dead spirit

1078
00:46:04,229 --> 00:46:06,083
你想吃　你还没这个本事呢
You're not qualified yet to eat it

1079
00:46:06,083 --> 00:46:07,041
哎　不会吧　师傅
Not really, Master.

1080
00:46:07,041 --> 00:46:09,208
狗肉穿肠过　徒弟的肚子好饿
Your pupil is very hungry

1081
00:46:15,750 --> 00:46:18,167
做做好事嘛　要留块骨头给我尝尝
Be kind enough to leave me at least a piece of bone

1082
00:46:18,542 --> 00:46:20,312
拜托
Please… be kind… please…

1083
00:46:20,312 --> 00:46:22,020
拜托嘛　师傅　拜托
Please… be kind… please…

1084
00:46:22,020 --> 00:46:22,958
别闹了
Go away

1085
00:46:22,958 --> 00:46:26,521
不就根毛吗　好了嘛　好了　拜托⋯
Be kind! Hey! Why not? Hey

1086
00:46:26,521 --> 00:46:28,917
拜托拜托嘛⋯我知道你还没有吞下去
Don't play! I know you haven't swallowed it

1087
00:46:28,917 --> 00:46:29,521
不要闹了嘛

1088
00:46:29,521 --> 00:46:30,708
你这个臭小子　除了要饭你还会什么　师傅　你给我一块嘛
You bastard,

1089
00:46:30,708 --> 00:46:31,916
你这个臭小子　除了要饭你还会什么　师傅　你给我一块嘛
how come you ain't that persistent apart from begging?

1090
00:46:31,916 --> 00:46:33,125
你这个臭小子　除了要饭你还会什么　师傅　你给我一块嘛
Help… C'mon…

1091
00:46:34,333 --> 00:46:34,958
师傅

1092
00:46:37,375 --> 00:46:39,333
师傅　你看
I need to get the rack.

1093
00:46:40,208 --> 00:46:41,187
出来了⋯

1094
00:46:41,187 --> 00:46:42,187
哎　记得下次再来
Remember to get back your underpants

1095
00:46:42,187 --> 00:46:43,042
换我了
Get it

1096
00:46:43,042 --> 00:46:43,917
哎　内裤拿走了没
Get it

1097
00:46:43,917 --> 00:46:44,458
拿了⋯

1098
00:46:44,458 --> 00:46:46,229
快点　你欢玩了　换我了啦
Why took so long? It's my turn.

1099
00:46:46,229 --> 00:46:47,041
来⋯
Come

1100
00:46:47,041 --> 00:46:47,958
小玉
Yuk

1101
00:46:48,625 --> 00:46:49,792
哎　怎么是你
It's you

1102
00:46:49,875 --> 00:46:53,250
你不但不听我的话　还变本加厉
You aren't listening to me and get even worse now

1103
00:46:53,250 --> 00:46:54,625
简直太不自爱
You have no self-respect at all

1104
00:46:54,625 --> 00:46:56,458
我全照你的吩咐做了
I've done as you told me

1105
00:46:56,917 --> 00:46:59,500
哎　你这个妓女就跟小贩一样当街叫卖
You are simply hawking yourself in the street

1106
00:46:59,500 --> 00:47:02,292
还好意思说照我的吩咐做
How dare you say you're doing as I said

1107
00:47:02,500 --> 00:47:05,375
没错　我是在卖豆腐
Wrong! I'm selling bean curd…

1108
00:47:10,792 --> 00:47:12,583
哇　真的卖豆腐咯
Really?

1109
00:47:13,375 --> 00:47:15,437
哎　快一点　你到底做不做生意了
Hurry up, are you doing business or not?

1110
00:47:15,437 --> 00:47:17,167
说好了干一次才跟你买豆腐的
We agreed to do once for buying a bowl of bean curd

1111
00:47:17,167 --> 00:47:18,354
不干是吧　退钱啊
No? Give me back the money…

1112
00:47:18,354 --> 00:47:19,437
别生气嘛　走⋯
No… I'll do it… Coming…

1113
00:47:19,437 --> 00:47:20,667
哎⋯来⋯
No… I'll do it… Coming…

1114
00:47:21,750 --> 00:47:23,437
多谢你的提醒啊
