1308
00:58:44,416 --> 00:58:47,042
真下贱　满身疮你都要　啊
That cheap? You even want one with sores?

1309
00:58:49,042 --> 00:58:50,125
看我的
Look

1310
00:58:51,167 --> 00:58:52,917
老大　早跟你说不是我
Big brother, I told you it wasn't me

1311
00:58:52,917 --> 00:58:53,708
你还不承认
You still deny it?

1312
00:58:53,708 --> 00:58:55,354
说不定只是长得很像而已嘛
Don't be mad! Maybe it's just likeness

1313
00:58:55,354 --> 00:58:56,833
他根本在装神弄鬼
You're pretending

1314
00:58:56,833 --> 00:58:58,042
我怎么有胡子嘛
Do I look like that moustached Singh?

1315
00:58:58,042 --> 00:58:58,771
刮了行不行
Maybe you shaved it off?

1316
00:58:58,771 --> 00:59:00,292
哪有人刮得那么快的
Who could do it so quickly?

1317
00:59:00,292 --> 00:59:02,021
哼　你胳膊肘子朝外拐
You're siding with a stranger

1318
00:59:02,021 --> 00:59:02,895
我讲道理啊
I talk sense

1319
00:59:02,895 --> 00:59:04,000
去死吧
Go to hell

1320
00:59:04,958 --> 00:59:05,729
你打伤人了嘛

1321
00:59:05,729 --> 00:59:06,750
打伤人又怎么样
See! You've hurt someone

1322
00:59:06,750 --> 00:59:07,687
你成心跟我过不去
What? Getting mad?

1323
00:59:07,687 --> 00:59:09,000
连老大的话都不听
What? Should I stand here and let you hit me?

1324
00:59:09,000 --> 00:59:10,083
哼　谁叫你大欺小
What? You dare disobey what the big brother tells you to do?

1325
00:59:10,083 --> 00:59:10,437
What? A big one bullies a small one?

1326
00:59:10,437 --> 00:59:11,812
我告诉你　我忍你很久了
- I've endured for a long time.    - Go to hell

1327
00:59:11,812 --> 00:59:15,354
喂⋯哎⋯不要打我老大⋯滚啊　你们
Don't beat my big brother! Go away

1328
00:59:15,354 --> 00:59:15,854
你滚吧

1329
00:59:15,854 --> 00:59:19,333
哎⋯不要打了⋯别打了⋯
Damn it! Again! Don't… Hey…

1330
00:59:19,333 --> 00:59:20,771
不要　救命啊
Don't

1331
00:59:20,771 --> 00:59:21,208
Help

1332
00:59:21,208 --> 00:59:21,937
哎　大爷　不要啊
Don't, master

1333
00:59:21,937 --> 00:59:22,833
让你开开眼界
Don't, master

1334
00:59:23,125 --> 00:59:24,542
求你放了她吧　大爷
Let her go, please, master

1335
00:59:29,583 --> 00:59:30,542
Siu Yuk…

1336
00:59:33,083 --> 00:59:33,875
小玉

1337
00:59:34,125 --> 00:59:36,792
救我
Help

1338
00:59:38,250 --> 00:59:40,542
我跟你拼了
Big head

1339
00:59:44,667 --> 00:59:45,917
大种
Dai Jung

1340
00:59:46,250 --> 00:59:47,083
哎哟　吓死我了

1341
00:59:47,250 --> 00:59:48,667
你进来怎么不敲门呢
Why didn't you knock?

1342
00:59:48,792 --> 00:59:50,250
哎　对不起啊　我找错人了
Sorry, I got the wrong place

1343
00:59:50,250 --> 00:59:51,354
记着关门啊　来　吃香蕉
Close the door

1344
00:59:51,354 --> 00:59:52,583
记着关门啊　来　吃香蕉
Have a banana

1345
00:59:52,583 --> 00:59:53,917
哎　对不起⋯
Sorry…

1346
00:59:56,333 --> 00:59:58,333
师傅　我⋯
Master…

1347
00:59:58,333 --> 00:59:59,771
这么久也不下来　找死
What's taken you so long? Wanna die?

1348
00:59:59,771 --> 01:00:01,229
都变回乞丐了　快点走啊
Things changed back to the original! Let's go

1349
01:00:01,229 --> 01:00:02,437
都变回乞丐了　快点走啊
Master, I can't move

1350
01:00:02,437 --> 01:00:03,625
走不动

1351
01:00:11,500 --> 01:00:13,292
啊　袁霸天
What? Yun Ba Tin

1352
01:00:18,625 --> 01:00:20,958
大种乞丐　赶紧死吧
Go to hell, Beggar Dai Jung

1353
01:00:25,542 --> 01:00:27,458
不要叫我大种　叫我朱大常
Don't call me Dai Jung

1354
01:00:27,458 --> 01:00:29,375
不要叫我大种　叫我朱大常
Call me Chow Yat Cheung

1355
01:00:35,958 --> 01:00:36,917
大种
Dai Jung

1356
01:00:38,500 --> 01:00:39,458
You've made us suffer a lot

1357
01:00:39,458 --> 01:00:40,749
大种　你不能死　要撑下去啊　大种
Dai Jung… you can't die!

1358
01:00:40,749 --> 01:00:42,166
大种　你不能死　要撑下去啊　大种
You must hang on

1359
01:00:42,166 --> 01:00:43,583
大种　你不能死　要撑下去啊　大种
Dai Jung… you can't die! Dai Jung

1360
01:00:43,583 --> 01:00:45,250
你没有法术了吗　嗯
You've no more magical powers?

1361
01:00:45,250 --> 01:00:47,000
明天有　明天你就知道厉害了
Tomorrow, I'll show you tomorrow

1362
01:00:47,000 --> 01:00:47,750
撒谎呢

1363
01:00:54,208 --> 01:00:55,500
王八蛋
Kill you, son of a bitch

1364
01:00:55,500 --> 01:00:58,562
把他脸反过来
- Turn his face over    - Turn his face

1365
01:00:58,562 --> 01:01:00,937
转过去⋯过去　再过去　看好
- Turn his face over    - Turn his face

1366
01:01:00,937 --> 01:01:01,208
Look

1367
01:01:09,542 --> 01:01:11,542
把眼睛睁开
Open his eyes

1368
01:01:17,500 --> 01:01:19,271
哎　滚吧
Master Tin said to let you go, but be careful in future

1369
01:01:19,271 --> 01:01:20,792
天爷说放你一马　你以后当心点
Master Tin said to let you go, but be careful in future

1370
01:01:20,792 --> 01:01:22,750
刚才看得真爽　眼睛都不眨一下啊
What a show it was just now You didn't even blink

1371
01:01:22,833 --> 01:01:23,958
不过刚才真的精采呀
Frankly… it was fascinating

1372
01:01:23,958 --> 01:01:25,083
不过刚才真的精采呀
Yes

1373
01:01:28,792 --> 01:01:32,500
这一次你还不死啊
You'll surely die this time

1374
01:01:34,708 --> 01:01:38,166
土地公⋯快点出来　你给我出来
God of Earth

1375
01:01:38,166 --> 01:01:41,625
土地公⋯快点出来　你给我出来
God of Earth, where are you? Come out quickly

1376
01:01:42,958 --> 01:01:46,416
哎⋯我不是来了嘛　干吗大呼小叫的
Hey… I'm here. Why shouting so loud?

1377
01:01:46,416 --> 01:01:48,042
要怎么样才可以救大种啊
How can I save Dai Jung?

1378
01:01:48,167 --> 01:01:50,208
人的生死早有定数
A man's fate is pre-determined One can't change Heaven's rules

1379
01:01:50,208 --> 01:01:52,229
天条规定改不了的
A man's fate is pre-determined One can't change Heaven's rules

1380
01:01:52,229 --> 01:01:53,520
哎呀　大种这次枉死
But he has suffered an innocent death because of me

1381
01:01:53,520 --> 01:01:54,771
我无论如何都要救他
I've got to bring him back no matter what

1382
01:01:54,771 --> 01:01:56,042
快点帮我想想办法
Help me to think of some ways

1383
01:01:56,042 --> 01:01:57,750
枉死一定是下地狱
An innocent death means going to hell

1384
01:01:58,250 --> 01:02:00,208
阎罗王这个人没得商量　不过⋯
King of Hades is strict

1385
01:02:00,208 --> 01:02:02,167
阎罗王这个人没得商量　不过⋯
But…

1386
01:02:02,375 --> 01:02:03,500
不过什么
Speak up

1387
01:02:03,708 --> 01:02:05,770
入枉死城之前
Before entering the City of Innocent Deaths,

1388
01:02:05,770 --> 01:02:08,375
有一段是邪神黑罗煞的地盘
There's an area governed by evil god Hak Lo Sat

1389
01:02:08,833 --> 01:02:10,917
他是专收孤魂野鬼的
He admits stray spirits

1390
01:02:11,250 --> 01:02:13,708
到了他的手上就永不得超生
Anyone in his hands never gets reincarnated

1391
01:02:14,208 --> 01:02:16,291
不过他是可以商量啰
But you may talk it over with him

1392
01:02:16,291 --> 01:02:17,625
哎　快点带我下去见见他
Bring me down to him quickly

1393
01:02:17,625 --> 01:02:21,208
哎呀　我只是一个小神　没有资格下去
Hey… I'm only a junior god and thus not eligible to go down

1394
01:02:21,208 --> 01:02:23,812
不像你　你有金身护着
Unlike you, you've a golden body for protection

1395
01:02:23,812 --> 01:02:25,625
上上下下都没问题
which makes you invulnerable

1396
01:02:26,542 --> 01:02:27,896
我马上把金身拿回来
I'll go and get the golden body back now

1397
01:02:27,896 --> 01:02:30,958
哎⋯千万不可以拿金身来开玩笑啊
Hey… don't make fun of the golden body

1398
01:02:30,958 --> 01:02:32,042
不行也得行
I must do what's necessary

1399
01:02:36,958 --> 01:02:37,833
干什么

1400
01:02:37,833 --> 01:02:39,083
哎呀　放手
What're you doing? Let go

1401
01:02:39,083 --> 01:02:41,146
师傅说　这个金身不能离开这间寺庙
Master said this golden body cannot leave the temple

1402
01:02:41,146 --> 01:02:43,291
哎呀　离开了又怎么样
What if it does?

1403
01:02:43,291 --> 01:02:43,937
不知道
- I don't know    - Then that means it's okay

1404
01:02:43,937 --> 01:02:44,521
那就是没事情
- I don't know    - Then that means it's okay

1405
01:02:44,521 --> 01:02:46,250
借来用用　最多付你利息
Let me borrow it, I'll pay you lots of interest

1406
01:02:46,417 --> 01:02:47,104
不可以
- No    - For just one night

1407
01:02:47,104 --> 01:02:47,687
只借一个晚上
- No    - For just one night

1408
01:02:47,687 --> 01:02:48,166
不行
- No    - One hour

1409
01:02:48,166 --> 01:02:48,646
一个时辰
- No    - One hour

1410
01:02:48,646 --> 01:02:49,375
不行
- No    - OK, then a cross

1411
01:02:49,375 --> 01:02:50,187
那就把你变个大字
- No    - OK, then a cross

1412
01:02:50,187 --> 01:02:51,667
不行　啊　怎么变
What cross?

1413
01:03:49,292 --> 01:03:50,417
大黑鬼　你给我站住
Hey man, halt

1414
01:03:50,417 --> 01:03:51,542
大黑鬼　你给我站住
Stand still

1415
01:03:51,833 --> 01:03:52,875
什么事
What's the matter?

1416
01:03:54,125 --> 01:03:55,000
放了他
Let him go

1417
01:03:55,042 --> 01:03:56,167
你是如来佛祖吗
Are you the Buddha?

1418
01:03:56,167 --> 01:03:57,125
不是
Are you the Buddha?

1419
01:03:57,125 --> 01:03:57,542
No

1420
01:03:57,542 --> 01:03:58,417
我呸
Damn

1421
01:04:07,167 --> 01:04:09,083
大黑鬼　你真没礼貌
Man, you're so rude. Let me tell you

1422
01:04:09,083 --> 01:04:10,479
我告诉你　我跟佛祖是好朋友
Man, you're so rude. Let me tell you

1423
01:04:10,479 --> 01:04:11,104
I'm friends with the Buddha

1424
01:04:11,104 --> 01:04:13,416
我代表他取回这个人的三魂七魄
I'll retrieve this person's spirit on his behalf,

1425
01:04:13,416 --> 01:04:14,542
听懂了没有
understand?

1426
01:04:16,875 --> 01:04:19,250
哎呀　你好大的胆子　不要过来⋯
How dare you? Stop

1427
01:04:19,250 --> 01:04:21,625
哎呀　你好大的胆子　不要过来⋯
Stop

1428
01:04:31,667 --> 01:04:34,292
垃圾　叫释迦牟尼来见我
Rubbish! Ask Sakyamuni to see me

1429
01:04:35,333 --> 01:04:37,583
不要走
Don't go…

1430
01:04:38,083 --> 01:04:40,354
其实我跟佛祖也不太熟
In fact, I'm not on good terms with Buddha

1431
01:04:40,354 --> 01:04:42,854
我也不知道你跟他有过节
I didn't know you and he had a grudge

1432
01:04:42,854 --> 01:04:44,146
这样子好了　我叫你老大
I'll take you for big brother

1433
01:04:44,146 --> 01:04:45,125
你已经有这么多的手下
I'll take you for big brother

1434
01:04:45,125 --> 01:04:47,229
多一个不多　少一个不少
Since you've so many men under you, having one more doesn't make a difference

1435
01:04:47,229 --> 01:04:49,583
这个就当送给我好了
This one… treat this as a gift to me

1436
01:04:49,583 --> 01:04:51,791
送给你有什么好处啊
What's in it for me?

1437
01:04:51,791 --> 01:04:52,792
好处
What's in it?

1438
01:04:53,208 --> 01:04:56,333
哎哟　我帮你修下脚趾甲　好长啊
How about… I'll pedicure for you, the nails are so long,

1439
01:04:56,333 --> 01:04:57,208
好不好
okay?

1440
01:04:57,208 --> 01:04:57,812
滚开

1441
01:04:57,812 --> 01:05:01,583
除非拿你的金身来换
Damn! Unless you exchange it with your golden body

1442
01:05:01,708 --> 01:05:04,125
金身　金身不可以给你
Golden body? I can't give it to you

1443
01:05:04,125 --> 01:05:05,667
况且你要来也没什么用啊
Besides, you've no use for it

1444
01:05:05,833 --> 01:05:07,250
摆着看也好啊
Just as a display

1445
01:05:07,250 --> 01:05:09,208
王八蛋　你个死黑鬼　好　换了
Bastard, you're going too far

1446
01:05:09,208 --> 01:05:11,167
王八蛋　你个死黑鬼　好　换了
Okay, exchange

1447
01:05:14,125 --> 01:05:16,417
大种　我再怎么样也要带你回去
Dai Jung, I must bring you back by any means

1448
01:05:16,583 --> 01:05:17,458
放心好了
Don't worry

1449
01:05:17,458 --> 01:05:18,708
把你金身留下来
Put down your golden body

1450
01:05:44,500 --> 01:05:45,791
你答应我要交换的
You promised to exchange with me

1451
01:05:45,791 --> 01:05:47,291
你居然还吸他的魂魄
Why have you taken his spirit?

1452
01:05:47,291 --> 01:05:48,792
我坏嘛
I'm a baddie

1453
01:06:02,292 --> 01:06:03,792
臭和尚　你跟鬼一样
Stinking monk, why appeared so sudden

1454
01:06:03,792 --> 01:06:05,292
从哪儿冒出来的
Stinking monk, why appeared so sudden

1455
01:06:05,292 --> 01:06:06,875
糟了　又回到上面来了
Damn, I'm back

1456
01:06:06,875 --> 01:06:08,917
你不喜欢的话　就回到下面去好了
If you don't like it, you can go back down

1457
01:06:08,917 --> 01:06:11,042
没有金身　我怎么回到下面去
How could I go down without the golden body?

1458
01:06:11,292 --> 01:06:12,812
哎呀　这下可惨了　连金身都被人家拿走
What a pity!

1459
01:06:12,812 --> 01:06:14,333
哎呀　这下可惨了　连金身都被人家拿走
He's even cheated me out of my golden body

1460
01:06:14,417 --> 01:06:16,687
大种⋯
Dai Jung…

1461
01:06:16,687 --> 01:06:18,958
大种⋯
Dai Jung…

1462
01:06:21,958 --> 01:06:23,375
大种
Dai Jung…

1463
01:07:03,708 --> 01:07:07,000
主公　我一定照你的吩咐
Lord, I'll do as you instruct me

1464
01:07:07,375 --> 01:07:09,583
帮你完成你的大业
and help accomplish your mission

1465
01:07:19,458 --> 01:07:20,250
有话好说嘛

1466
01:07:21,458 --> 01:07:22,292
不要这样好不好

1467
01:07:22,833 --> 01:07:26,583
拜托⋯先留下来　有话慢慢说嘛
Hey… don't be like that?

1468
01:07:26,583 --> 01:07:28,000
你们不要这样嘛
Hey… brothers…

1469
01:07:29,375 --> 01:07:30,917
怎么连这点面子都不给
Won't give me a face?

1470
01:07:31,042 --> 01:07:33,125
好歹我也是这儿当家的
I'm in charge here

1471
01:07:34,875 --> 01:07:36,270
早跟你说过不要这么做的嘛
I told you not to do this

1472
01:07:36,270 --> 01:07:37,292
怎么回事啊
What's the matter?

1473
01:07:37,500 --> 01:07:39,291
里面那票神仙说
As you have consorted with evil spirits,

1474
01:07:39,291 --> 01:07:41,000
这一次你跟邪魔打交道
the fairies inside said…

1475
01:07:41,000 --> 01:07:42,271
他们都不愿意跟你在一起了
the fairies inside said…

1476
01:07:42,271 --> 01:07:43,500
…they don't want to be with you

1477
01:07:43,500 --> 01:07:45,312
所以呢　全都跑光了
They've all gone These just returned to get their luggage.

1478
01:07:45,312 --> 01:07:47,208
这一群人是回来搬行李的
They've all gone These just returned to get their luggage.

1479
01:07:47,208 --> 01:07:49,062
对不起啊　为了我的终身俸
Sorry, for my life-long emoluments,

1480
01:07:49,062 --> 01:07:50,291
只好跟着大家走了　看着办吧　啊
Sorry, for my life-long emoluments,

1481
01:07:50,291 --> 01:07:51,583
I have to follow them… goodbye

1482
01:08:03,125 --> 01:08:06,542
搞什么鬼啊　东西呢
What's happening? Where's the stuff?

1483
01:08:07,250 --> 01:08:09,042
济癫　那个金身呢
Mad Monk, where's the golden body?

1484
01:08:11,042 --> 01:08:13,333
你死定了　惹这么大的祸
Oh no! You've caused big trouble

1485
01:08:16,875 --> 01:08:19,125
糟了　土地公也不见了
Oh no! Even God of Earth is gone.

1486
01:08:19,125 --> 01:08:20,416
哎呀　这次祸闯大了
We're in deep shit now

1487
01:08:20,416 --> 01:08:21,750
哎呀　这次祸闯大了
Oh no…

1488
01:08:31,250 --> 01:08:33,208
师傅　快走了　师傅　快走吧

1489
01:08:38,750 --> 01:08:40,208
师傅　你要到哪儿去
Master, where are you going?

1490
01:08:40,208 --> 01:08:42,187
济癫　我早跟你说过
Mad Monk, as I told you,

1491
01:08:42,187 --> 01:08:44,375
那个金身是不能离开寺庙
the golden body cannot leave the temple

1492
01:08:44,375 --> 01:08:46,333
现在弄得人神共愤
Now you've caused anger among men and gods

1493
01:08:46,333 --> 01:08:48,792
我怎么担得起呀
how can I bear this responsibility?

1494
01:08:48,792 --> 01:08:50,375
师傅⋯快走吧⋯待会儿打雷下来⋯
Master, leave quickly

1495
01:08:50,375 --> 01:08:52,583
师傅⋯
Thunder may split the temple

1496
01:08:56,542 --> 01:08:57,667
啊

1497
01:08:59,500 --> 01:09:01,166
阿弥陀佛⋯
