01:21:29,791 --> 01:21:30,750
把你一个人留在寺庙里面
At such a critical moment, I shouldn't have left you on your own

1692
01:21:30,750 --> 01:21:32,708
你知道我处境危险　你干吗回来找我
Why care to come back for me if you know the danger?

1693
01:21:34,583 --> 01:21:36,875
因为我一直最欣赏的人就是你
Because you're the one person I admire most

1694
01:21:38,833 --> 01:21:40,042
快走
Come again! Let's go quickly

1695
01:21:44,167 --> 01:21:46,500
师傅　我的金身所剩无几
Master, there's not much left of my golden body

1696
01:21:46,500 --> 01:21:47,750
只有使出最后一招
I must use the last resort

1697
01:21:47,750 --> 01:21:49,437
将剩下来的金粉打入黑罗煞身体
I'll fight the remainder into his body

1698
01:21:49,437 --> 01:21:50,583
才能制服他
to overpower him

1699
01:21:50,708 --> 01:21:52,625
金身耗尽　你也会被毁灭
You'll perish too when your golden body is used up

1700
01:21:52,625 --> 01:21:54,146
顾不了这么多了
No time to be bothered with that

1701
01:21:54,146 --> 01:21:55,750
那你怎么打入他体内
How are you going to do it?

1702
01:21:55,750 --> 01:21:57,708
只有麻烦你把他的嘴张开
Just help me to open his mouth

1703
01:21:57,875 --> 01:21:58,750
这么简单
That simple?

1704
01:21:58,750 --> 01:21:59,354
行不行
Can you?

1705
01:21:59,354 --> 01:22:00,542
当然不行
Of course not

1706
01:22:11,042 --> 01:22:13,417
师傅⋯你怎么了
Master… Are you alright, master?

1707
01:22:14,000 --> 01:22:15,417
我的钵
My bowl

1708
01:22:15,667 --> 01:22:17,333
金粉呢　师傅　你该不会是⋯
Where's the golden powder?

1709
01:22:17,333 --> 01:22:18,916
金粉呢　师傅　你该不会是⋯
Master, didn't you…

1710
01:22:18,916 --> 01:22:20,812
是啊　我全吞下去了
Yes, I swallowed it all

1711
01:22:20,812 --> 01:22:24,000
啊　在这么危急的关头　你竟然⋯
At such a critical moment, you…

1712
01:22:24,000 --> 01:22:25,479
我也不愿意啊
I didn't want to either.

1713
01:22:25,479 --> 01:22:28,542
吞了这些金粉　我肚子觉得怪怪的
My stomach feels strange now

1714
01:22:37,625 --> 01:22:39,104
师傅　你快点想想办法　把金粉拉出来
Master, think of a quick way

1715
01:22:39,104 --> 01:22:40,541
师傅　你快点想想办法　把金粉拉出来
to defecate the golden powder

1716
01:22:40,541 --> 01:22:42,167
我长期便秘
But I'm always constipated

1717
01:22:47,208 --> 01:22:48,125
我想起来了
I remember now

1718
01:22:48,125 --> 01:22:49,708
金身还有两颗金牙在我嘴里
I've still got two golden teeth

1719
01:22:55,042 --> 01:22:56,667
啊　好　偷东西
You stole them?

1720
01:22:56,667 --> 01:22:58,458
嘘　我没牙　借用一下嘛
I have no teeth so I just borrowed them

1721
01:23:00,083 --> 01:23:01,750
撑不住了
I can't hang on any longer… please do my last favour

1722
01:23:01,750 --> 01:23:03,125
师傅　帮我最后一个忙
I can't hang on any longer… please do my last favour

1723
01:23:03,125 --> 01:23:04,917
想办法把他嘴巴张开
- What?    - Find a way to open his mouth

1724
01:23:08,583 --> 01:23:11,667
我决定使尽浑身解数来收拾你
I decide to use all my magic to overpower you

1725
01:23:11,917 --> 01:23:13,417
我好怕哟
I feel very scared

1726
01:23:13,417 --> 01:23:15,104
哼　怕了吧
Scared?

1727
01:23:15,104 --> 01:23:17,291
那跪下磕三个响头　我就饶了你
Kneel and bow three times

1728
01:23:17,291 --> 01:23:18,125
and I'll spare you

1729
01:23:18,500 --> 01:23:24,625
Haha…

1730
01:23:24,833 --> 01:23:26,333
笑得好过瘾嘛
What a funny laugh

1731
01:23:27,125 --> 01:23:28,458
济癫
Mad Monk…

1732
01:23:31,917 --> 01:23:37,000
济癫⋯
Mad Monk…

1733
01:24:11,875 --> 01:24:22,083
阿弥陀佛　南无阿弥陀佛
Amida Buddha…

1734
01:24:34,958 --> 01:24:38,083
早就说了嘛⋯他一定会输的⋯
See, I said he's bound to lose

1735
01:24:38,083 --> 01:24:39,458
输定了⋯不会赢的⋯
- I also said he'll lose    - Lose for sure,

1736
01:24:39,458 --> 01:24:40,958
输定了⋯不会赢的⋯
no argument…

1737
01:24:40,958 --> 01:24:42,750
输定
Lose? Why would you think that?

1738
01:24:42,750 --> 01:24:44,542
就像大种乞丐
Lose? Why would you think that?

1739
01:24:44,542 --> 01:24:46,500
本来还有二十多年的饭可以讨
Just like Beggar Dai Jung,

1740
01:24:46,500 --> 01:24:48,000
现在不但死了　临死还是个乞丐
he could have twenty more years to beg for his living

1741
01:24:48,000 --> 01:24:49,458
现在不但死了　临死还是个乞丐
Now he's not only dead, he died as a beggar

1742
01:24:49,458 --> 01:24:52,292
他害得那个〝野鸡〞刮破了脸　好可怜呢
Also, that whore was disfigured. What a pity

1743
01:24:52,292 --> 01:24:54,520
还有袁霸天那件事就更惨了
The case of Yun Ba Tin is worse still

1744
01:24:54,520 --> 01:24:56,958
临死之前呢　还多伤了几十条人命
Tens of lives were lost before he died

1745
01:24:56,958 --> 01:24:58,521
你说这个⋯该怎么说呢
So… it's so… so…

1746
01:24:58,521 --> 01:25:00,125
你说这个⋯该怎么说呢
How should I say it?

1747
01:25:00,125 --> 01:25:01,041
失败⋯失败呀⋯
What a failure

1748
01:25:01,041 --> 01:25:01,770
失败⋯失败呀⋯
Yes, failure

1749
01:25:01,770 --> 01:25:02,479
何止失败
Not only a failure.

1750
01:25:02,479 --> 01:25:03,916
如果那天让我跟他单挑　打败了他
If you let me beat him in a duel on that day,

1751
01:25:03,916 --> 01:25:06,062
就不会让他弄得一团糟了
things wouldn't have been such a mess

1752
01:25:06,062 --> 01:25:07,062
你算了吧　整天都说单挑
Nonsense…

1753
01:25:07,062 --> 01:25:08,292
你算了吧　整天都说单挑
Stop mentioning the duel

1754
01:25:08,583 --> 01:25:10,791
虽然大种是冤枉死的
No doubt Beggar Dai Jung

1755
01:25:10,791 --> 01:25:12,104
不过在他临死之前
suffered an innocent death

1756
01:25:12,104 --> 01:25:14,000
起码知道自己叫朱大常了
But before he died, he knew his name was Chow Yat Cheung

1757
01:25:14,000 --> 01:25:16,375
那就是他重新得回他的自尊
It means he got back his pride

1758
01:25:16,667 --> 01:25:19,625
你们看看
- Look…    - Something to watch…

1759
01:25:19,625 --> 01:25:21,833
这一辈子他不用再做乞丐
- He doesn't have to be a beggar this life    - Right…

1760
01:25:29,292 --> 01:25:30,833
小玉的脸虽然花了

1761
01:25:31,292 --> 01:25:32,937
但是她再也不做〝野鸡〞

1762
01:25:32,937 --> 01:25:35,583
而是真正的在卖豆腐
Though Siu Yuk was defaced,

1763
01:25:35,583 --> 01:25:37,833
she's no longer a whore

1764
01:25:37,833 --> 01:25:39,750
She's really selling bean curd now

1765
01:25:39,750 --> 01:25:40,854
至于无恶不作的袁霸天
As for the villain Yun Ba Tin

1766
01:25:40,854 --> 01:25:41,854
大家都知道
As for the villain Yun Ba Tin

1767
01:25:41,854 --> 01:25:44,333
他在临死前忏悔是不想再做人
We all know that when he died

1768
01:25:44,333 --> 01:25:46,125
现在他已经转入轮回了
he said he didn't want to be a human being anymore

1769
01:25:46,125 --> 01:25:48,750
He's now reincarnated

1770
01:25:49,375 --> 01:25:52,667
今世做猪嘛　前途一片光明啊
In this life he’s a pig, he's got a bright future

1771
01:25:53,375 --> 01:25:55,416
请大家想一想
Let us think did Dragon Fighter win or lose?

1772
01:25:55,416 --> 01:25:57,229
降龙究竟是输还是赢呢
Let us think did Dragon Fighter win or lose?

1773
01:25:57,229 --> 01:25:58,917
哎⋯这⋯
Well…

1774
01:25:58,917 --> 01:26:00,792
不管怎么样
No matter what, Dragon Fighter Lo Han no longer exists

1775
01:26:00,792 --> 01:26:02,500
降龙罗汉已经不存在了
No matter what, Dragon Fighter Lo Han no longer exists

1776
01:26:02,500 --> 01:26:04,791
啊⋯这只是开玩笑嘛⋯
You've dropped something

1777
01:26:04,791 --> 01:26:07,250
啊⋯这只是开玩笑嘛⋯
Lucky I pick up for you

1778
01:26:07,250 --> 01:26:09,958
不过又多了一个降龙尊者
But now we have a senior Dragon Fighter

1779
01:26:13,750 --> 01:26:14,604
Why are you here?

1780
01:26:14,604 --> 01:26:17,729
不会吧⋯他都可以当尊者⋯
- He'll be a senior    - Could he be a senior?

1781
01:26:17,729 --> 01:26:18,917
Right

1782
01:26:18,917 --> 01:26:20,500
一不小心就升级了
A promotion for a few grades only

1783
01:26:23,292 --> 01:26:25,167
加冕仪式开始
The coronation ceremony begins

1784
01:27:00,375 --> 01:27:01,625
恭喜你
Congratulations

1785
01:27:01,625 --> 01:27:03,042
谢谢
Thank you

1786
01:27:21,958 --> 01:27:24,979
降龙　今天你成为降龙尊者
What's your goal being made

1787
01:27:24,979 --> 01:27:26,500
有什么感想
a senior Dragon Fighter today?

1788
01:27:26,750 --> 01:27:30,104
我想成为一位和平使者
I want to be an emissary of peace and be Heaven's envoy to spread love throughout the world

1789
01:27:30,104 --> 01:27:32,312
代表天宫向凡间宣扬爱心
And let them know that with love, anywhere is a paradise.

1790
01:27:32,312 --> 01:27:34,583
让他们明白
And let them know that with love, anywhere is a paradise.

1791
01:27:35,125 --> 01:27:38,000
只要有爱　哪里都是天堂
